tement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20rationalized%20it%20this%20way.%20If%20anybody%20that%20has%20much%20better%20than%20me%20in%20their%20own%20field%2C%20not%20necessarily%20in%20my%20field%2C%20I%20would%20respect%2C%20I%20would%20call%20them%2C%20and%20I%20would%20say%2C%20where%20do%20you%20think%20I%20was%20wrong%20in%20saying%20this%3F%20But%20I%20didn't%20find.%20A%20lot%20of%20my%20western%20friends%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20NRIs%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20good%20people%20in%20India%20called%20me%2C%20and%20without%20exception%2C%20they%20were%20all%20very%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Ftrends%2Fnarayana-murthy-defends-70-hour-work-week-remark-lot-of-western-friends-called-12000431.html%5C%22%3ECNBC-TV18%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhilanthropist%20and%20author%20Sudha%20Murty%2C%20being%20interview%20alongside%20her%20husband%2C%20said%20a%2070-hour%20work%20week%20was%20common%20for%20her%20family%20and%20revealed%20that%20he%20regularly%20used%20worked%20as%20many%20as%2090%20hours%20in%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20he%20has%20never%20given%20advice%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20doing%20it%20myself%20first%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Murthy%20shared%20details%20of%20his%20rigorous%20work%20routine%20at%20Infosys%2C%20where%20he%20worked%20for%2085-90%20hours%20every%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20go%20(to%20work)%20six%20and%20a%20half%20days.%20Even%20in%20the%20electronics%20area%2C%20I%20used%20to%20work%20six%20and%20a%20half%20days.%20And%20every%20day%20I%20would%20leave%20home%20at%206%20a.m.%20in%20the%20morning.%20I%20would%20be%20in%20the%20office%20at%206.20.%20And%20I%20would%20leave%20by%20about%208.15%2C%208.30%20pm%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Infosys%20founder%20courted%20controversy%20when%20he%20appealed%20to%20youngster%20in%20India%20to%20work%2070%20hours%20a%20week.%20The%20comment%20was%20critic