ater-noida-housing-society-4802865%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-stray-dogs-chase-woman-in-greater-noida-housing-society-4802865%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jeffrey%20Epstein%20Sex%20Scandal%3A%20What%20New%20Documents%20Reveal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJeffrey%20Epstein%20loved%20to%20socialise%20with%20the%20world's%20elite%20before%20and%20after%20he%20was%20exposed%20as%20a%20sex%20trafficker%20and%20a%20paedophile%2C%20show%20a%20new%20batch%20of%20documents%20presented%20in%20court%20today.%20The%20investigation%20documents%2C%20which%20were%20previously%20sealed%2C%20detail%20how%20the%20financier%20leveraged%20his%20connections%20with%20the%20rich%20and%20famous%20to%20recruit%20his%20victims%20and%20cover%20up%20his%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20New%20York%20judge%20on%20Wednesday%20began%20unsealing%20the%20identities%20of%20people%20linked%20to%20the%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20case%2C%20the%20US%20financier%20who%20killed%20himself%20in%202019%20as%20he%20awaited%20trial%20for%20sex%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20stem%20from%20a%202015%20civil%20suit%20by%20Virginia%20Giuffre%2C%20who%20says%20she%20was%20one%20of%20the%20many%20young%20girls%20trafficked%20by%20Epstein%20and%20his%20partner%2C%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20notable%20inclusions%20in%20the%20documents%2C%20which%20include%20almost%201%2C000%20pages%20of%20depositions%20and%20statements%2C%20were%20former%20US%20presidents%20Bill%20Clinton%20and%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20physicist%20Stephen%20Hawking%2C%20and%20pop%20star%20Michael%20Jackson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20include%20the%20testimony%20of%20Epstein's%20former%20butler%20Alfredo%20Rodriquez%2C%20who%20recalled%20paying%20cash%20to%20young%20girls%20who%20visited%20Epstein's%20property%20in%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20Florida%2C%20and%20Johanna%20Sjoberg%2C%20who%20claimed%20Prince%20Andrew%20placed%20a%20hand%20on%20her%20breast%20once%20at%20Epstein's%20house.%20Sjoberg%20testified%20that%20Epstein%20told%20her%20%E2%80%9CClinton%20likes%20them%20young%2C%20referring%20to%20girls%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20one%20unsealed%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20set%20of%20declassified%20information%20had%20accounts%20of%20some%20of%20Epstein's%20victims%20who%20took%20payments%20of%20%24200%20to%20give%20him%20and%20his%20friends%20massages.%20Most%20of%20his%20young%20victims%20were%20high%20school%20students%2C%20the%20documents%20reveal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20also%20include%20an%20email%20exchange%20between%20Epstein%20accuser%20Giuffre%20and%20journalist%20Sharon%20Churcher.%20In%20the%202011%20exchange%2C%20Churcher%20tells%20Giuffre%20that%20she%20is%20correct%20to%20be%20concerned%20about%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20side%26quot%3B%20Vanity%20Fair%20was%20taking%20in%20a%20story%20involving%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiuffre%20responds%20with%20an%20unsubstantiated%20claim%20that%20Bill%20Clinton%20stormed%20into%20Vanity%20Fair%20and%20threatened%20the%20magazine%20over%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20doing%20some%20research%20into%20VF%20yesterday%2C%20it%20does%20concern%20me%20what%20they%20could%20want%20to%20write%20about%20me%20considering%20that%20B.Clinton%20walked%20into%20VF%20and%20threatened%20them%20not%20to%20write%20sex-trafficing%20%5Bsic%5D%20articles%20about%20his%20good%20friend%20J%20E%2C%26quot%3B%20Giuffre%20wrote%20in%20her%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiuffre%2C%20who%20now%20lives%20in%20Australia%2C%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20outspoken%20Epstein%20victims%2C%20drawing%20attention%20to%20high-profile%20individuals%20who%20were%20in%20Epstein's%20orbit.%20In%20her%20suit%20against%20Prince%20Andrew%2C%20she%20claimed%20he%20was%20one%20of%20several%20powerful%20men%20to%20whom%20Epstein%20%26quot%3Blent%26quot%3B%20her%20for%20abuse.%20The%20royal%20family%20later%20stripped%20King%20Charles'%20younger%20brother%20of%20his%20honorific%20titles%20and%20royal%20patronages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEpstein%20was%20charged%20with%20sex%20trafficking%20in%20July%202019%20but%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20a%20Manhattan%20prison%20cell%20before%20he%20could%20stand%20trial.%20Maxwell%20is%20serving%20a%2020-year%20sentence%20for%20sex%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704429060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F7o9cl6l_jeffrey-epstein-afp_625x300_05_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjeffrey-epstein-sex-scandal-what-new-documents-reveal-4803397%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jeffrey%20Epstein%20loved%20to%20socialise%20with%20the%20world's%20elite%20before%20and%20after%20he%20was%20exposed%20as%20a%20sex%20trafficker%20and%20a%20paedophile%2C%20show%20a%20new%20batch%20of%20documents%20presented%20in%20court%20today%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjeffrey-epstein-sex-scandal-what-new-documents-reveal-4803397%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjeffrey-epstein-sex-scandal-what-new-documents-reveal-4803397%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjeffrey-epstein-sex-scandal-what-new-documents-reveal-4803397%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Christopher%20Nolan%E2%80%99s%20Peloton%20Instructor%20Has%20Seen%20%E2%80%98Oppenheimer%E2%80%99%20Twice%2C%20Still%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Understand%20%E2%80%98Tenet%E2%80%99%3A%20%E2%80%98That%20S%E2%80%94%20Went%20Right%20Over%20My%20Head%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704428879000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Foppenheimer-tenet-split.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235862310%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Christ