0a%20handgun%20and%20a%20shotgun.%20Students%20barricaded%20in%20offices%2C%20ducked%20into%20classrooms%2C%20and%20fled%20in%20panic%20as%20he%20started%20firing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20killing%20a%20student%20and%20injuring%205%2C%20he%20turned%20the%20gun%20on%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20at%20the%20school%2C%20Butler%20had%20posted%20a%20TikTok%20video%20from%20the%20school%20bathroom%20just%20before%20he%20went%20on%20a%20rampage.%20He%20captioned%20the%20post%20%26quot%3BNow%20we%20wait%26quot%3B%20while%20the%20song%20'Stray%20Bullet'%20played%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20song%2C%20by%20the%20German%20rock%20band%20KMFDM%2C%20features%20lyrics%20like%20%26quot%3BI'm%20your%20nightmare%20coming%20true%2C%20I%20am%20your%20worst%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BStray%20bullet%2C%20from%20the%20barrel%20of%20love%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fpqa7lv1o_dylan-butler-us-school-shooter_625x300_05_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20other%20photos%20of%20Butler%20posing%20with%20firearms%20were%20found%20by%20investigators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECops%20suspect%20that%20he%20planned%20to%20kill%20many%20more%20as%20an%20improvised%20explosive%20device%20was%20found%20on%20his%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20are%20yet%20to%20provide%20a%20motive%20for%20the%20shooting.%20Two%20of%20his%20friends%20told%20The%20Associated%20Press%20that%20he%20was%20a%20quiet%20person%20who%20had%20been%20bullied%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20hurting.%20He%20got%20tired.%20He%20got%20tired%20of%20the%20bullying.%20He%20got%20tired%20of%20the%20harassment.%20Was%20it%20a%20smart%20idea%20to%20shoot%20up%20the%20s