20removed%20the%20death%20penalty%20handed%20down%20to%20Indians%20and%20sentenced%20them%20to%20prison%20for%20varying%20durations%20ranging%20from%20three%20to%2025%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20had%20noted%20on%20December%2028%2C%202023%20the%20%E2%80%9Cverdict%20today%20of%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20of%20Qatar%20in%20the%20Dahra%20Global%20case%2C%20in%20which%20the%20sentences%20have%20been%20reduced%E2%80%9D.%20Stating%20that%20a%20detailed%20judgement%20was%20awaited%2C%20the%20MEA%20had%20then%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cin%20close%20touch%20with%20the%20legal%20team%20as%20well%20as%20the%20family%20members%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20next%20steps%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20weekly%20briefing%20on%20Thursday%2C%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20that%20the%20legal%20team%20had%20received%20the%20court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20confirmed%20that%20each%20individual%20has%20received%20different%20sentences.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20for%20the%20next%20steps%2C%20there%20is%20a%2060-day%20period%20during%20which%20this%20matter%20can%20be%20appealed%20to%20the%20Court%20of%20Cassation%2C%20which%20is%20the%20highest%20court%20of%20Qatar.%20Our%20legal%20team%20is%20working%20on%20this%20issue%2C%20and%20we%20are%20in%20discussion%20with%20the%20families%20and%20the%20legal%20team%2C%20we%20are%20connected%20with%20them%20and%20will%20see%20what%20unfolds%20next%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2026%2C%20the%20veterans%2C%20detained%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20were%20sentenced%20to%20death%20by%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20Court%20of%20First%20Instance.%20Hired%20by%20the%20now-defunct%20Omani%20private%20company%20Dahra%20Global%20Technologies%20and%20Consultancy%20Services%2C%20they%20were%20contracted%20to%20provide%20training%20and%20related%20services%20to%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20armed%20forces.%20Although%20the%20charges%20have%