ive%20sessions%2C%20making%20it%20the%20shortest%20match%20in%20the%20format%20ever%20(in%20terms%20of%20number%20of%20balls%20bowled)%2C%20there%20have%20been%20question%20marks%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20pitch.%20On%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20match%2023%20wickets%20fell.%20Both%20India%20and%20South%20Africa%20batters%20found%20the%20going%20tough.%20They%20gave%20better%20account%20of%20themselves%20in%20the%20second%20innings%2C%20yet%20a%20two-day%20Test%20match%20was%20beyond%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rohit%20Sharma%20did%20not%20criticise%20the%20Newlands%20pitch%20directly%2C%20he%20was%20upfront%20in%20slamming%20the%20attack%20that%20Indian%20pitches%20come%20under%2C%20particularly%20for%20its%20spinning%20nature.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20here%20to%20play%20Test%20cricket%2C%20you%20talk%20about%20Test%20cricket%20the%20ultimate%20prize%20and%20pinnacle%2C%20and%20then%20you%20should%20stand%20by%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20are%20put%20up%20like%20a%20challenge%20like%20that%2C%20you%20should%20come%20and%20face%20it.%20In%20India%2C%20day%20one%20the%20pitch%20starts%20turning%2C%20they%20keep%20talking%20about%20'puff%20of%20dust%2C%20puff%20of%20dust.%20So%20much%20crack%20here%20on%20the%20pitch'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20England%20opener%20Chris%20Broad%20was%20the%20ICC%20match%20referee%20for%20the%20two-Test%20series%20and%20Rohit%20believes%20that%20global%20body's%20empanelled%20referees%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bneutral%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20Real%20Aggression%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnProper%20belting%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnOH%20CAPTAIN%20MY%20CAPTAIN%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FRohitSharma%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23RohitSharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7T53SfVWcx%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F7T53SfVWcx%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Tanish%20Singh%20(%40tanishsingh0508)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftanishsingh0508%2Fstatus%2F1742967983960473735%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20we%20stay%20neutral%20everywhere%20we%20go%2C%20especially%20the%20match%20referees.%20Some%20of%20these%20match%20referees%20are%2C%20they%20need%20to%20keep%20their%20eyes%20on%20how%20they%20rate%20pitches%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20skipper%20quite%20aggressively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICC%20match%20referee%20Andy%20Pycroft's%20%26quot%3Baverage%26quot%3B%20rating%20for%20pitch%20used%20for%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20final%20in%20Ahmedabad%20also%20did%20not%20go%20down%20well%20with%20Rohit%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20can't%20believe%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%20pitch%20was%20rated%20'below%20average'%20(average%20actually).%20A%20batter%20got%20a%20hundred%20there.%20How%20can%20that%20be%20a%20poor%20pitch%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20The%20ICC%20and%20the%20match%20referees%20need%20to%20looking%20into%20it.%20Start%20Rating%20pitches%20based%20on%20what%20they%20see%20and%20not%20based%20on%20countries%20(hosting).%20I%20hope%20they%20keep%20their%20eyes%20and%20ears%20open%20and%20look%20into%20those%20aspects.%20I%20am%20all%20for%20pitches%20like%20this%20(like%20the%20one%20at%20Newlands).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20pride%20ourselves%20playing%20on%20pitches%20like%20these%2C%20all%20I%20want%20to%20say%20is%20be%20neutral.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20of%20mistrust%20for%20some%20of%20the%20select%20match%20officials%20was%20evident%20when%20Rohit%20sarcastically%20said%20that%20he%20would%20love%20to%20know%20about%20the%20parameters%20match%20referees%20use%20to%20rate%20pitches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20see%20the%20how%20the%20pitch%20has%20been%20rated.%20I%20want%20to%20see%20it%20now.%20I%20want%20to%20see%20the%20chart%2C%20how%20they%20rate%20pitches.%20Clearly%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Cape%20Town%2C%20Centurion%2C%20all%20are%20different.%20Pitches%20deteriorate%20fast%2C%20overhead%20conditions%20are%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20ball%20seams%20from%20ball%20one%2C%20that's%20okay%2C%20but%20if%20the%20ball%20starts%20turning%E2%80%A6.%20If%20the%20ball%20starts%20turning%2C%20they%20don't%20like%20it.%20If%20you%20want%20the%20ball%20only%20to%20seam%20and%20not%20turn%2C%20it's%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20seen%20enough%20of%20cricket%20now.%20I%20have%20seen%20enough%20of%20how%20these%20match%20referees%20looks%20into%20these%20ratings%2C%20I%20have%20no%20issues%20with%20how%20they%20want%20to%20note%2C%20they%20have%20to%20be%20neutral.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704424140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fvot489ro_rohit-sharma-pc_625x300_05_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fbe-neutral-furious-rohit-sharma-slams-icc-match-referees-indicates-bias-against-india-4801038%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20Rohit%20Sharma%20did%20not%20criticise%20the%20Newlands%20pitch%20directly%2C%20he%20was%20upfront%20in%20slamming%20the%20attack%20that%20Indian%20pitches%20come%20under%2C%20particularly%20for%20its%20spinning%20nature.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fbe-neutral-furious-rohit-sharma-slams-icc-match-referees-indicates-bias-against-india-4801038%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn