South%20Africa%202nd%20Test%20ended%20inside%20two%20days.%20In%20all%2C%20only%20five%20days%20of%20cricket%20action%20was%20possible%20to%20see%20in%20the%20two-match%20Test%20series.%20While%20the%20first%20Test%20ended%20in%20three%20days%2C%20the%20second%20Test's%20duration%20was%20beyond%20explanation.%20Thrice%20the%20teams%20were%20all%20out%20in%20a%20span%20of%20five%20sessions.%20While%20the%20pitch%20at%20the%20Newlands%20Stadium%20is%20under%20question%2C%20there%20are%20those%20who%20have%20raised%20questions%20at%20the%20batters'%20technique%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20different%20take%20on%20batters%20prowess.%20He%20feels%20that%20not%20just%20fast%20and%20bouncy%20pitches%20(like%20in%20the%20SENA%20countries)%20but%20the%20batter's%20real%20Test%20comes%20in%20spinning%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20what%20Test%20cricket%20is%20all%20about.%20You%20are%20going%20to%20be%20tested.%20And%20I%20honestly%20believe%20I've%20always%20believed%20that%20if%20you%20cannot%20play%20on%20pitches%20where%20the%20ball%20turns%20into%20the%20batter%2C%20you%20know%20there%20is%20a%20tendency%20amongst%20the%20SENA%20country's%20media%2C%20particularly%20if%20you%20think%20that%20you%20know%2C%20if%20you%20can't%20play%20on%20fast%2C%20bouncy%20pitches%2C%20you're%20not%20a%20batter%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fstory%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2nd-test-day-one-23-wickets-sunil-gavaskar-sena-media-2484201-2024-01-04%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20sorry.%20You%20are%20not%20a%20batter%20if%20you%20can't%20play%20the%20turning%20pitch%20because%20over%20here%20for%20the%20bouncy%20pitch%2C%20there%20are%20two%20movements%20here.%20There%20for%20four%20spinners%2C%20where%20the%20ball%20is%20turning%2C%20you've%20got%20to%20go%20down%20the%20pitch.%20You've%20got%20to%20use%20the%20crease.%20All%20the%20shots%20can%20be%20exhibited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20that's%20you%20know%20what%3F%20I%20think%2C%20sadly%2C%20you%20know%2C%20our%20media%20should%20be%20actually%20writing%20about%20this.%20You%20know%2C%20our%20media%20should%20be%20talking%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20know%2C%20but%20our%20media%20is%20so%20dependent%20sometimes%2C%20not%20all%20the%20time%2C%20on%20getting%20interviews%20with%20players%2C%20so%20they%20do%20not%20want%20to%20upset%20anybody.%20So%20they%20will%20not%20question%20the%20batting%20ability%20of%20some%20of%20the%20overseas%20guys%20because%20of%20that.%20But%20that's%20the%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Aiden%20Markram%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64634-aiden-kyle-markram-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAiden%20Markram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20perhaps%20played%20his%20best%20Test%20knock%20in%20the%20most%20challenging%20conditions%2C%20said%20that%20throughout%20his%20103-ball%20106%2C%20he%20felt%20that%20he%20could%20get%20out%20anytime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20this%20track%2C%20it%20did%20seem%20as%20if%20attack%20is%20the%20best%20form%20of%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertainly%20in%20some%20cases%20for%20sure%20(attack%20is%20the%20best%20form%20of%20defence).%20Kind%20of%20feels%20like%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20you%20get%20out.%20You%20have%20to%20maximise%20and%20score%20when%20you're%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSqueeze%20a%2050%2C%20it%20might%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20tough%20conditions.%20Roles%20and%20partnerships.%20Some%20person%20might%20have%20to%20hang%20around%20and%20let%20another%20guy%20score.%26quot%3B%20Markram%20had%20no%20hesitation%20in%20admitting%20that%20getting%20bowled%20out%20for%2055%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20was%20unacceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGood%20show%3F%20Certainly%20not%2055.%20It%20was%20very%20hard.%20Sometimes%20you%20find%20yourself%20nicking%20every%20ball.%20Felt%20like%20it%20was%20one%20of%20those%20days%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20back%20in%20hindsight%2C%20we%20could%20have%20worked%20towards%20150.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20a%20good%20game.%20Difficult%20to%20come%20back%20from%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704424080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-03%2Fdp5fg9d_sunil-gavaskar-bcci_625x300_05_March_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fyou-are-not-a-batter-sunil-gavaskars-hard-hitting-take-after-india-vs-south-africa-2nd-test-4801360%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20vs%20South%20Africa%3A%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20feels%20that%20not%20just%20fast%20and%20bouncy%20pitches%20(like%20in%20the%20SENA%20countries)%20but%20the%20batter's%20real%20Test%20comes%20in%20spinning%20conditions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fyou-are-not-a-batter-sunil-gavaskars-hard-hitting-take-after-india-vs-south-africa-2nd-test-4801360%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fyou-are-not-a-batter-sunil-gavaskars-hard-hitting-take-after-india-vs-south-africa-2nd-test-4801360%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fyou-are-not-a-batter-sunil-gavaskars-hard-hitting-take-after-india-vs-south-africa-2nd-test-4801360%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222nd%20Test%3A%20India%20register%20first-ever%20Test%20win%20at%20Newlands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%