ws%2Fwas-bobby-deols-animal-fight-scene-with-ranbir-kapoor-ripped-off-from-his-2001-movie-aashiq-watch%2Farticleshow%2F106557440.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20Defence%20Minister%20Unveils%20Plan%20For%20Post-War%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20on%20Thursday%20presented%20his%20plan%20for%20the%20post-war%20administration%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20saying%20neither%20Hamas%20nor%20Israel%20would%20govern%20the%20Palestinian%20territory%20after%20hostilities%20there%20conclude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGallant%20unveiled%20an%20outline%20of%20his%20plan%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bday%20after%26quot%3B%20the%20war%20to%20the%20press%20before%20submitting%20it%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20war%20cabinet%2C%20which%20has%20been%20divided%20in%20recent%20weeks%20over%20the%20future%20of%20Gaza%20after%20the%20ouster%20of%20Hamas%2C%20which%20has%20ruled%20the%20strip%20since%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20plan%2C%20Israel's%20war%20in%20the%20territory%20will%20continue%20until%20it%20has%20secured%20the%20return%20of%20the%20hostages%20taken%20on%20October%207%2C%20dismantled%20Hamas's%20%26quot%3Bmilitary%20and%20governing%20capabilities%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20removed%20any%20remaining%20military%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20the%20outline%20says%2C%20a%20new%20phase%20will%20begin%20during%20which%20%26quot%3BHamas%20will%20not%20control%20Gaza%20and%20will%20not%20pose%20a%20security%20threat%20to%20the%20citizens%20of%20Israel%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20local%20Palestinian%20bodies%20assuming%20the%20territory's%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20would%20reserve%20its%20right%20to%20operate%20inside%20the%20territory%2C%20the%20plan%20states%2C%20but%20there%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bno%20Israeli%20civilian%20presence%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20after%20the%20goals%20of%20the%20war%20have%20been%20achieved