%20cost%20in%20what%20they%20say%20is%20a%20protest%20against%20Israel's%20military%20operations%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthi%20campaign%20has%20been%20extraordinarily%20disruptive%20to%20international%20shipping%2C%20causing%20some%20companies%20to%20suspend%20transits%20through%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20instead%20take%20the%20much%20longer%2C%20costlier%20journey%20around%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVice%20Admiral%20Brad%20Cooper%2C%20who%20leads%20U.S.%20Naval%20forces%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20told%20reporters%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20Houthi%20exploding%20boat%20drove%20out%20about%2050%20miles%20(80%20km)%20into%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20then%20detonated%20in%20dense%20shipping%20lanes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20came%20within%20a%20couple%20of%20miles%20of%20ships%20operating%20in%20the%20area%20-%20merchant%20ships%20and%20U.S.%20Navy%20ships%20-%20and%20we%20all%20watched%20as%20it%20exploded%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooper%20told%20reporters%2C%20adding%20the%20target%20of%20the%20attack%20was%20not%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECooper%20said%20there%20have%20now%20been%2025%20attacks%20by%20the%20Houthis%20against%20merchant%20vessels%20transiting%20the%20southern%20Red%20Sea%20and%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20and%20added%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20no%20signs%20that%20their%20irresponsible%20behavior%20is%20abating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20repeated%20Houthi%20attacks%20have%20increased%20pressure%20on%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20to%20respond%20militarily%2C%20something%20his%20administration%20has%20been%20reluctant%20to%20do%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20escalating%20already%20soaring%20regional%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERetired%20four-star%20Marine%20general%20Frank%20McKenzie%2C%20who%20led%20U.S.%20forces%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20until%20retiring%20in%202022%2C%20said%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20response%20to%20attacks%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20against%20U.S.%20troops%20at%20bases%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Syria%20has%20been%20too%20%26quot%3Btentative%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bunfocused.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20reset%20deterrence%2C%20we%20must%20apply%20violence%20that%20Tehran%20understands%2C%26quot%3B%20McKenzie%20wrote%20in%20an%20Op-Ed%20published%20on%20Thursday%20in%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20and%20other%20countries%20last%20month%20launched%20Operation%20Prosperity%20Guardian%20to%20protect%20civilian%20vessels%2C%20which%20Cooper%20said%20now%20included%20contributions%20from%2022%20countries.%20So%20far%2C%20Cooper%20said%20U.S.%20warships%20and%20U.S.%20partners%20have%20shot%20down%20two%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20six%20anti-ship%20ballistic%20missiles%20and%2011%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20U.S.%20warships%20sank%20three%20Houthi%20speed%20boats%20to%20protect%20a%20commercial%20vessel%20from%20being%20hijacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20Biden%20administration%20official%20told%20reporters%20on%20Wednesday%20%26quot%3Bif%20that%20happened%20again%2C%20we%20would%20probably%20do%20the%20exact%20same%20thing.%26quot%3B%20The%20same%20official%2C%20speaking%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20said%20the%2012-nation%20statement%20to%20the%20Houthis%20was%20very%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20not%20anticipate%20another%20warning%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20a%20U.S.%20representative%20told%20the%20U.N.%20Security%20Council%20the%20United%20States%20believed%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20had%20reached%20an%20%26quot%3Binflection%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20Operation%20Prosperity%20Guardian%20might%20target%20Houthi%20positions%20with%20strikes%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20attacking%20ships%2C%20Cooper%20said%20that%20the%2022-nation%20coalition%20was%20purely%20defensive%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnything%20that%20happens%20outside%20of%20the%20defensive%20aspect%20of%20this%20operation%20is%20a%20completely%20different%20operation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis%20have%20said%20their%20attacks%20on%20commercial%20shipping%20target%20vessels%20with%20Israeli%20links%20or%20were%20sailing%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20many%20vessels%20have%20had%20no%20Israeli%20connection%20and%20were%20not%20bound%20for%20Israeli%20ports%2C%20and%20major%20shipping%20lines%20have%20suspended%20their%20operations%20through%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECooper%20said%20the%20ships%20that%20have%20been%20attacked%20have%20direct%20connections%20to%2055%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20regardless%20of%20the%20vessel's%20company%20ownership%20or%20its%20destination%2C%20these%20Houthi%20attacks%20are%20for%20sure%20destabilizing%20and%20contrary%20to%20international%20law%20and%20clearly%20...%20must%20stop%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704422880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fr08jmkr8_houthi-military-chopper-reuters_625x300_05_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhouthi-drone-boat-explodes-in-red-sea-hours-after-us-consequences-warning-4802899%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Houthi%20drone%20boat%20packed%20with%20explosives%20detonated%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20on%20Thursday%20but%20failed%20to%20cause%20any%20damage%20or%20casualties%2C%20the%20US%20Navy%20said%2C%20as%20the%20Yemen-based%20group%20continued%20its%20attacks%20in%20defiance%20of%20international%20calls%20to%20stop.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhouthi-drone-boat-explodes-in-red-sea-hours-after-us-consequences-warning