puppet%20of%20him%20at%20Epstein's%20Manhattan%20townhouse.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20then%20I%20sat%20on%20Andrew's%20lap%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20on%20my%20own%20volition%2C%20and%20they%20took%20the%20puppet's%20hands%20and%20put%20it%20on%20Virginia's%20breast%20and%20so%20Andrew%20put%20his%20on%20mine%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrince%20Andrew%20couldn't%20be%20reached%20for%20comment%20Thursday.%20He%20reached%20a%20civil%20settlement%20with%20Giuffre%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20previously%20confidential%20documents%20related%20to%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20have%20been%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESeveral%20previously%20confidential%20documents%20related%20to%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20have%20been%20made%20public.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHere%20is%20what%20we%20learned%20so%20far%20from%20the%2040%20unsealed%20documents%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5E69XTX6tf%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5E69XTX6tf%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FONDsUBS8dV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FONDsUBS8dV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Bloomberg%20(%40business)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbusiness%2Fstatus%2F1743028263297990836%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClinton%2C%20Trump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Bill%20Clinton's%20ties%20to%20Epstein%20have%20been%20the%20source%20of%20much%20speculation%20since%20photographs%20and%20records%20emerged%20of%20Clinton%20traveling%20on%20the%20late%20money%20manager's%20private%20jet.%20The%20unsealed%20documents%20provide%20a%20little%20more%20context%20as%20to%20how%20the%20former%20president's%20name%20became%20wrapped%20up%20in%20the%20litigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiuffre%20told%20a%20journalist%20that%20she%20had%20dinner%20with%20Clinton%20at%20Epstein's%20villa%20in%20the%20US%20Virgin%20Islands%20but%20did%20not%20allege%20he%20did%20anything%20untoward.%20In%20Giuffre's%20unpublished%20deposition%20transcript%2C%20mentioned%20in%20the%20unsealed%20documents%2C%20she%20referred%20to%20Clinton%20%26quot%3Bteasing%20the%20girls%20on%20either%20side%20of%20him%20with%20playful%20pokes%20and%20brassy%20comments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiuffre's%20lawyers%20sought%20to%20depose%20Clinton%2C%20but%20Maxwell's%20attorneys%20said%20the%20dinner%20party%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bconcocted%20story%26quot%3B%20that%20had%20been%20debunked%20by%20a%20former%20FBI%20director%20who%20reviewed%20Clinton's%20movements%20in%20January%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESjoberg%20also%20claimed%20in%20her%20deposition%20that%20Epstein%20told%20her%20%26quot%3BClinton%20likes%20them%20young%2C%20referring%20to%20girls%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20one%20unsealed%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEpstein%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20draw%20powerful%20and%20influential%20people%20into%20his%20orbit%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20say%20they%20now%20regret%20ever%20being%20associated%20with%20him.%20Sjoberg%20said%20she%20was%20on%20Epstein's%20private%20plane%20once%20when%20it%20had%20to%20land%20in%20Atlantic%20City%2C%20New%20Jersey.%20Epstein%20remarked%20%26quot%3Bgreat%2C%20we'll%20call%20up%20Trump%26quot%3B%20and%20go%20to%20the%20casino%2C%20referring%20to%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESjoberg%20recalled%20Epstein%20%26quot%3Bname-dropping%26quot%3B%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Clinton%20referred%20to%20his%202019%20statement%2C%20claiming%20he%20had%20never%20been%20to%20been%20to%20Epstein's%20Virgin%20Islands%20complex%2C%20and%20knew%20nothing%20of%20Epstein's%20terrible%20crimes.%20He%20did%20take%20four%20trips%20on%20Epstein's%20private%20plane%20to%20Europe%2C%20Asia%20and%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20didn't%20respond%20to%20the%20latest%20documents%2C%20but%20has%20previously%20said%20that%20he%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bfalling%20out%26quot%3B%20with%20Epstein%20and%20wasn't%20%26quot%3Ba%20fan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDubin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHedge%20fund%20manager%20Glenn%20Dubin%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Eva%20Andersson-Dubin%2C%20have%20long%20been%20identified%20as%20Epstein's%20friends%20but%20denied%20any%20knowledge%20of%20his%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiuffre%20claimed%20in%20her%20deposition%20that%20Maxwell%20sent%20her%20to%20give%20Dubin%20a%20massage%20one%20day%20in%20Palm%20Beach%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20unsealed%20portion%20of%20Maxwell's%20deposition%2C%20she%20denied%20this.%20%26quot%3BJust%20for%20the%20record%2C%20I%20have%20never%20at%20any%20time%2C%20at%20anyplace%2C%20in%20any%20moment%20ever%20asked%20Virginia%20Roberts%20or%20whatever%20she%20is%20called%20now%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20anybody%2C%26quot%3B%20Maxwell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESjoberg%20testified%20that%20she%20gave%20the%20Dubins%20massages%20once%20at%20their%20apartment%20on%20Breakers%20Row%20in%20Palm%20Beach%20%26quot%3Bbut%20there%20was%20nothing%20sexual.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Dubins%20said%20on%20Thursday%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Dubins%20strongly%20deny%20these%20allegations%2C%20as%20we%20first%20said%20in%202019%2C%20when%20these%20unsubstantiated%20statements%20first%20surfaced%20as%20part%20of%20this%20same%20civil%20court%20proceeding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndersson-Dubin%2C%20who%20was%20also%20an%20ex-girlfriend%20of%20Epstein's%2C%20testified%20as%20a%20character%20witness%20at%20Maxwell's%20sex-trafficking%20trial%2C%20telling%20the%20jury%20she%20was%20comfortable%20with%20her%20own%20children's%20relationship%20with%20the%20financier%2C%20and%20called%20him%20%26quot%3BUncle%20F.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20more%3A%20Who%20Was%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%2C%20and%20Who%20Was%20Linked%20to%20Him%3F%3A%20QuickTake%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaxwell%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiuffre's%20suit%20accused%20Maxwell%20of%20recruiting%20her%20at%20the%20age%20of%2016%20to%20be%20sexually%20abused%20by%20Epstein.%20After%20Maxwell%20called%20her%20a%20liar%2C%20Giuffre%20sued%20her%20for%20defamation%20in%202015.%20The%20unsealed%20documents%20were%20filed%20during%20that%20case%2C%20which%20settled%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Maxwell%20was%20convicted%20of%20sex%20trafficking%20conspiracy%20and%20is%20serving%2020%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20material%20showed%20how%20Epstein%20wanted%20to%20offer%20a%20reward%20to%20any%20of%20Giuffre's%20friends%20or%20family%20who%20could%20%26quot%3Bprove%20her%20allegations%20are%20false.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20strongest%20is%20the%20Clinton%20dinner%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20%26quot%3BGmax%26quot%3B%20in%202015%2C%20which%20also%20mentioned%20theoretical%20physicist%20Stephen%20Hawking%20participating%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Borgy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEpstein%20also%20suggested%20Maxwell%20issue%20a%20lengthy%20public%20statement%20to%20distance%20herself%20from%20him%20after%20he%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20soliciting%20a%20minor%20for%20prostitution%20in%20Florida%20in%202008.%20She%20never%20issued%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaxwell%20denied%20knowledge%20of%20Epstein's%20efforts%20to%20discredit%20Giuffre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHawking%2C%20who%20suffered%20from%20major%20physical%20disabilities%20due%20to%20Amyotrophic%20Lateral%20Sclerosis%2C%20died%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaxwell's%20attorney%2C%20Arthur%20Aidala%2C%20said%20his%20client%20took%20no%20position%20on%20the%20decision%20to%20unseal%20the%20documents%20and%20was%20focused%20on%20her%20appeal.%20%26quot%3BShe%20has%20consistently%20and%20vehemently%20maintained%20her%20innocence%2C%26quot%