ge%20in%20the%20martial%20status%20of%20the%20petitioner.%20The%20petitioner%20has%20become%20a%20widow%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20psychiatric%20evaluation%20report%20of%20the%20AIIMS%20indicates%20that%20the%20petitioner%20is%20suffering%20from%20extreme%20trauma%20due%20to%20the%20death%20of%20her%20husband%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Prasad%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20petitioner%20can%20result%20in%20the%20petitioner%20losing%20her%20mental%20balance%20and%20she%20can%20harm%20herself%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Prasad%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20Court%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%2C%20at%20this%20juncture%2C%20the%20petitioner%20should%20be%20permitted%20to%20terminate%20her%20pregnancy%20because%20allowing%20the%20petitioner%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20pregnancy%20can%20impair%20the%20mental%20stability%20of%20the%20petitioner%20as%20she%20is%20showing%20suicidal%20tendencies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccordingly%2C%20the%20petitioner%20is%20permitted%20to%20undergo%20the%20procedure%20for%20termination%20of%20her%20pregnancy%20at%20AIIMS.%20AIIMS%20is%20requested%20to%20conduct%20the%20procedure%20even%20though%20the%20petitioner%20has%20crossed%20her%20gestation%20period%20of%2024%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%20in%20the%20judgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20passing%20the%20judgement%2C%20the%20bench%20referred%20to%20the%20law%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20Apex%20Court%20in%20X%20vs.%20Principal%20Secretary%2C%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20Department%2C%20Govt.%20of%20NCT%20of%20Delhi%20and%20Another%2C%20wherein%20it%20held%20that%20it%20is%20the%20prerogative%20of%20each%20woman%20to%20evaluate%20her%20life%20and%20arrive%20at%20the%20best%20course%20of%20action%20in%20view%20of%20the%20change%20in%20material%20circumstances%20and%20also%20in%20view%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20right%20to%20reproductive%20choice%20also%20includes%20the%20right%20not%20to%20procreate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20this%20order%20has%20been%20passed%20in%20light%20of%20the%20peculiar%20facts%20and%20circumstances%20of%20the%20present%20case%20and%20the%20same%20should%20not%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20precedent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20reserved%20the%20order%20on%20the%20plea%20after%20hearing%20the%20submissions%20of%20the%20petitioner's%20counsel%20and%20further%20psychiatric%20evaluation%20of%20the%20petitioner%20reserved%20the%20order%20for%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20counsel%2C%20Dr.Amit%20Mishra%2C%20submitted%20before%20the%20court%20that%20she%20was%20admitted%20in%20the%20hospital%20but%20she%20left%20as%20the%20doctors%20were%20persuading%20her%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForcing%20her%20to%20continue%20the%20pregnancy%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20her%20privacy%2C%20her%20counsel%20submitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20had%20observed%20that%20the%20apex%20court%20judgement%20allowed%20termination%20even%20at%20this%20stage.%20The%20petitioner's%20mental%20status%20has%20now%20changed%20the%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20vacation%20bench%20of%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20had%20called%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Psychiatry%20of%20the%20AIIMS%20Hospital%20as%20to%20whether%2C%20in%20her%20state%20of%20severe%20depression%20with%20suicidal%20ideation%2C%20it%20would%20be%20detrimental%20to%20her%20health%20if%20this%20pregnancy%20is%20permitted%20to%20be%20continued%20for%20its%20full%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20considering%20the%20psychiatric%20evaluation%20report%20from%20AIIMS%2C%20vacation%20judge%20Neena%20Krishna%20Bansal%20ordered%20a%20further%20psychiatric%20evaluation%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Psychiatry%20of%20the%20AIIMS%20Hospital%20filed%20a%20report%20stating%20that%20the%20petitioner%20was%20evaluated%20on%20December%2028%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20found%20to%20be%20suffering%20from%20severe%20depression%20with%20suicidal%20ideation%2C%20the%20report%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20view%20of%20the%20risk%20to%20self%20and%20others%20(foetus)%2C%20the%20patient%20and%20family%20were%20advised%20admission%2C%20to%20which%20they%20agreed.%20The%20patient%20is%20admitted%20in%20psychiatry%20ward%20in%20AIIMS%20Hospital%2C%20the%20bench%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20had%20directed%20AIIMS%20to%20conduct%20a%20psychiatric%20evaluation%20of%20a%2023-year-old%20widow%20who%20has%20sought%20a%20permission%20for%20medical%20termination%20of%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20medical%20board%20had%20not%20recommended%20a%20medical%20termination%20of%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20issuing%20directions%2C%20the%20bench%20heard%20the%20submission%20of%20Advocate%20Dr%20Amit%20Mishra%2C%20counsel%20for%20petitioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20submitted%20before%20the%20court%20that%20she%20is%20facing%20mental%20trauma%20due%20to%20the%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20judgements%20that%20allow%20the%20termination%20of%20pregnancy%20at%20an%20advanced%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20submitted%20that%20the%20petitioner%20is%20facing%20mental%20and%20physical%20trauma.%20Even%20so%2C%20she%20is%20not%20able%20to%20take%20a%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2023-year-old%20woman%20has%20approached%20the%20court.%20It%20is%20stated%20that%20her%20husband%20had%20died%20on%20October%209%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2022%2C%202023%2C%20the%20bench%20had%20asked%20the%20AIIMS%20to%20constitute%20a%20medical%20board%20and%20to%20examine%20the%20petitioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20had%20been%20directed%20to%20give%20a%20report%20as%20to%20whether%20the%20petitioner%20is%20in%20a%20condition%20to%20undergo%20the%20procedure%20for%20termination%20of%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704418920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Ft72t3c1g_delhi-high-court-650_625x300_11_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-allows-widow-suffering-from-mental-trauma-to-terminate-pregnancy-4801557%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20permitted%20a%20widow%20to%20medically%20terminate%20her%2027-week%20pregnancy%20after%20considering%20the%20change%20in%20circumstances%20and%20her%20mental%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-allows-widow-suffering-from-mental-trauma-to-terminate-pregnancy-4801557%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-allows-widow-suffering-from-mental-trauma-to-terminate-pregnancy-4801557%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-allows-widow-suffering-from-mental-trauma-to-terminate-pregnancy-4801557%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Antony%20Blinken%20To%20Visit%20Israel%20As%20Regional%20War%20Fears%20Mount%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20will%20head%20Thursday%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20as%20fears%20mount%20that%20Israel's%20war%20in%20Gaza%20will%20spread%20across%20the%20region%2C%20following%20deadly%20blasts%20in%20Iran%20and%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Hamas%20leader%20in%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20US%20official%20speaking%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20confirmed%20the%20trip%20--%20Blinken's%20fourth%20to%20the%20region%20since%20the%20start%20of%20Israel's%20war%20against%20Hamas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20--%20but%20declined%20to%20offer%20any%20details%20on%20the%20itinerary%20apart%20from%20a%20stop%20in%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20came%20after%20at%20least%2095%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20more%20than%20200%20wounded%20in%20Iran%20by%20twin%20explosions%20near%20the%20grave%20of%20a%20slain%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20general%2C%20with%20Hamas%20backer%20Tehran%20quickly%20blaming%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Israel%20for%20the%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20rejected%20suggestions%20of%20either%20nation's%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20US%20official%20told%20AFP%20that%20an%20unclaimed%20strike%20the%20night%20before%20that%20claimed%20the%20life%20of%20Hamas's%20number%20two%20in%20a%20Beirut%20suburb%20had%20been%20the%20work%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20announcement%20of%20Blinken's%20visit%2C%20State%20Department%20spokesman%20Matthew%20Miller%20echoed%20the%20fears%20of%20many%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%20about%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20expanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20in%20no%20one's%20interest%20--%20not%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20any%20country%20in%20the%20region%2C%20not%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20any%20country%20in%20the%20world%20--%20to%20see%20this%20conflict%20escalated%20any%20further%20than%20it%20already%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20visit%20Wednesday%20to%20the%20Lebanese%20border%2C%20where%20Israeli%20forces%20have%20regularly%20traded%20fire%20with%20Iran-backed%20Hezbollah%2C%20Israeli%20army%20chief%20Herzi%20Halevi%20said%20troops%20were%20%26quot%3Bin%20very%20high%20readiness%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHostilities%20also%20threatened%20to%20expand%20to%20Yemen%20after%20the%20United%20States%20and%20its%20allies%20jointly%20warned%20the%20country's%20Huthi%20rebels%20of%20unspecified%20consequences%20unless%20they%20immediately%20halted%20attacks%20on%20Red%20Sea%20shipping%20carried%20out%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20not%20anticipate%20another%20warning%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20US%20official%20said%2C%20calling%20the%20message%20%26quot%3Bvery%20clear%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20against%20Hamas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20was%20triggered%20by%20its%20bloody%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20around%201%2C140%20people%2C%20most%20of%20them%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20based%20on%20official%20Israeli%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFighters%20also%20took%20around%20250%20hostages%20back%20to%20Hamas-run%20Gaza%2C%20129%20of%20whom%20remain%20in%20captivity%2C%20according%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Israel%20vowed%20to%20destroy%20the%20group%2C%20launching%20a%20relentless%20bombardment%20and%20ground%20invasion%20that%20has%20reduced%20swathes%20of%20Gaza%20to%20rubble%20and%20claimed%20at%20least%2022%2C313%20lives%2C%20according%20to%20the%20territory's%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20estimates%201.9%20million%20Gazans%20are%20displaced%2C%20and%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20has%20warned%20of%20the%20risk%20of%20famine%20and%20disease%2C%20with%20only%20a%20minimal%20amount%20of%20aid%20entering%20the%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBitter%20enemies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWednesday's%20blasts%20in%20Iran%20struck%20mourners%20commemorating%20slain%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20general%20Qasem%20Soleimani%20on%20the%20fourth%20anniversary%20of%20his%20death%20in%20a%20US%20drone%20strike%2C%20official%20media%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran's%20Supreme%20leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20blamed%20%26quot%3Bevil%20and%20criminal%20enemies%20of%20the%20Iranian%20nation%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20bombings%2C%20and%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20disaster%20will%20have%20a%20harsh%20response%2C%20God%20willing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Israeli%20military%20spokesman%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20explosions%2C%20while%20the%20State%20Department's%20Miller%20called%20any%20suggestion%20of%20US%20involvement%20%26quot%3Bridiculous%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20Washington%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20reason%20to%20believe%20that%20Israel%20was%20involved%26quot%3B%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegional%20tensions%20had%20already%20been%20soaring%20following%20Tuesday's%20strike%20in%20Lebanon%20on%20Hamas%20number%20two%20Saleh%20al-Aruri%2C%20the%20most%20high-profile%20figure%20to%20be%20killed%20since%20the%20start%20of%20Israel's%20war%20against%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20and%20Iran%20have%20long%20been%20bitter%20enemies%2C%20and%20violence%20involving%20Iran-backed%20groups%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Syria%20and%20Yemen%20has%20spiked%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETehran%20also%20blames%20Israel%20for%20a%20December%20strike%20in%20Syria%20that%20killed%20Razi%20Moussavi%2C%20a%20senior%20commander%20in%20the%20Quds%20Force%2C%20the%20same%20branch%20of%20the%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20that%20Soleimani%20once%20headed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20intense%20wider%20warfare%20has%20so%20far%20been%20avoided%2C%20the%20latest%20blasts%20in%20Iran%20rattled%20global%20markets%2C%20sending%20oil%20prices%20up%20by%20more%20than%20three%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20vowed%20that%20the%20killing%20of%20Aruri%20and%20six%20other%20Hamas%20operatives%20on%20its%20home%20turf%20will%20not%20go%20unpunished%2C%20labelling%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20serious%20assault%20on%20Lebanon...%20and%20a%20dangerous%20development%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20leader%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20warned%20Israel%20against%20all-out%20war%20on%20its%20northern%20neighbour%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20televised%20speech%20he