last%20year%2C%20it%20has%20traversed%20about%203.7%20million%20kilometers%20as%20it%20went%20about%20a%20circuitous%20route%20to%20reach%20its%20%26quot%3Bkarambhoomi%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bland%20of%20action%26quot%3B.%20ISRO%20says%20Aditya%20is%20healthy%20and%20scientific%20results%20have%20already%20started%20flowing%20in%20as%20it%20has%20beamed%20back%20beautiful%20images%20of%20the%20full%20disc%20of%20the%20Sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya's%20home%20is%20in%20a%20halo-shaped%20orbit%2C%20some%201.5%20million%20kilometers%20away%20from%20Earth.%20Although%20closer%20to%20the%20Sun%20than%20the%20Earth%2C%20the%20orbit%20will%20still%20be%20far%2C%20far%20away%2C%20since%20the%20Sun%20is%20some%20150%20million%20kilometers%20away%20from%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F63k32ij4_india-solar-mission-aditya-l1-isro-solar-mission-ani_625x300_23_December_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20its%20final%20vantage%20point%20which%20is%20called%20the%20Lagrangian%20Point-1%2C%20the%201%2C475%20kilogram%20Aditya-L1%20satellite%20will%20conduct%20scientific%20experiments%20to%20better%20understand%20the%20star%20of%20our%20solar%20system%2C%20which%20remains%20an%20enigma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20solar%20observatory%20will%20have%20an%20uninterrupted%20and%20continuous%20view%20of%20the%20Sun%20and%20will%20help%20us%20understand%20space%20weather.%20It%20will%20act%20like%20a%20forecasting%20and%20warning%20platform%20for%20solar%20storms%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nigar%20Shaji%2C%20the%20Project%20Director%20for%20Aditya-L1%20satellite%20at%20the%20U%20R%20Rao%20Satellite%20Center%2C%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20solar%20storm%20is%20a%20large-scale%20magnetic%20eruption%20on%20the%20Sun%2C%20which%20can%20effect%20the%20entire%20solar%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20Aditya-L1%20will%20look%20at%20Sun%20continuously%2C%20it%20can%20warn%20us%20of%20imminent%20solar%20electro-magnetic%20effects%20on%20Earth%20and%20protect%20our%20satellites%2C%20and%20other%20power%20electrical%20and%20communications%20networks%20from%20getting%20disrupted.%20This%20will%20help%20continue%20normal%20operations%20by%20operating%20them%20in%20safe%20modes%2C%20till%20the%20solar%20storm%20passes%20by%2C%26quot%3B%20S%20Somanath%2C%20Chairman%2C%20ISRO%2C%20told%20NDTV%2C%20adding%20that%20India%20has%20assets%20worth%20over%20Rs%2050%2C000%20crores%20in%20space%20including%20over%2050%20operational%20satellites%20that%20need%20to%20be%20protected%20against%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20Sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fna6sctm_aditya-l1-sun-images_625x300_05_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAditya-L1%20satellite%20will%20act%20as%20a%20space-based%20protector%20of%20sorts%2C%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20solar%20flares%20and%20ensuing%20solar%20storms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20large%20solar%20flare%20comes%20out%20of%20the%20Sun%2C%20it%20can%20fry%20the%20electronics%20of%20the%20satellites.%20To%20protect%20them%2C%20space%20engineers%20shutdown%20the%20electronics%20and%20keep%20them%20in%20safe%20shutdown%20state%20till%20the%20highly-charged%20storm%20passes%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAditya-L1%20is%20an%20intelligent%20satellite.%20It%20will%20never%20sleep%20and%20will%20keep%20a%20hawk's%20eye%20on%20the%20activities%20of%20Earth's%20nearest%20star%20to%20warn%20when%20the%20Sun's%20wrath%20will%20impact%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Prof%20Somak%20Raychaudhury%2C%20astrophysicist%20at%20Ashoka%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf%20Durgesh%20Tripathi%2C%20a%20scientist%20at%20Inter-University%20Centre%20for%20Astronomy%20and%20Astrophysics%20(IUCAA)%20in%20Pune%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20complex%20space%20telescope%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20opportunity%20for%20scientists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Scientific%20Suite%20on%20Aditya-L1%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20says%20in%20its%20statement%20that%20the%20major%20scientific%20objectives%20of%20Aditya-L1%20mission%20are%20to%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStudy%20solar%20upper%20atmospheric%20(chromosphere%20and%20corona)%20dynamics%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStudy%20chromospheric%20and%20coronal%20heating%2C%20the%20physics%20of%20the%20partially%20ionized%20plasma%2C%20the%20initiation%20of%20the%20coronal%20mass%20ejections%2C%20and%20flares%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EObserve%20the%20in-situ%20particle%20and%20plasma%20environment%2C%20providing%20data%20for%20the%20study%20of%20particle%20dynamics%20from%20the%20Sun%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStudy%20the%20physics%20of%20solar%20corona%20and%20its%20heating%20mechanism%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDiagnostics%20of%20the%20coronal%20and%20coronal%20loops%20plasma%3A%20Temperature%2C%20velocity%20and%20density%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDevelopment%2C%20dynamics%20and%20origin%20of%20CME%20(Coronal%20Mass%20Ejections)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIdentify%20the%20sequence%20of%20processes%20that%20occur%20at%20multiple%20layers%20(chromosphere%2C%20base%20and%20extended%20corona)%20which%20eventually%20leads%20to%20solar%20eruptive%20events%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMagnetic%20field%20topology%20and%20magnetic%20field%20measurements%20in%20the%20solar%20corona%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20origin%2C%20composition%20and%20dynamics%20of%20solar%20wind%2C%20the%20drivers%20for%20space%20weather%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%