a%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-indicted-new-york-stormy-daniels-hush-money-payment-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20allegedly%20falsifying%20business%20documents%20to%20hide%20a%202016%20hush-money%20payment%20to%20porn%20actress%20Stormy%20Daniels%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20because%20he%20was%20acting%20on%20legal%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20in%20court%20filings%20and%20public%20statements%20that%20he%20is%20blameless%20in%20what%20he's%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BStormy%20nonsense%26quot%3B%20because%20he%20placed%20%26quot%3Bfull%20Reliance%20on%20the%20JUDGEMENT%20%26amp%3B%20ADVICE%20OF%20COUNCIL%20%5Bsic%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20put%20it%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrdering%20Trump%20to%20give%20advance%20notice%20of%20an%20advice-of-counsel%20defense%20%26quot%3Bwill%20avoid%20the%20risk%20of%20significant%20trial%20disruption%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24253964-hush-money-da-advice-of-counsel-motion-20231215%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elead%20prosecutor%20Matthew%20Colangelo%20wrote%20to%20Manhattan%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Juan%20Merchan.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20additionally%20want%20Merchan%20to%20order%20Trump%20to%20%26quot%3Bproduce%20all%20discoverable%20communications%20related%20to%20that%20defense%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20those%20between%20Trump%20and%20any%20relevant%20attorneys%2C%20by%20the%20same%20February%2012%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24253947-hush-money-trump-advice-of-counsel-filing-20240104%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBut%20in%20a%20response%20filed%20on%20Thursday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Trump's%20lawyers%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20wait%20until%20other%20pretrial%20motions%20are%20decided%20before%20he'll%20formally%20disclose%20if%20he'll%20seek%20an%20advice-of-counsel%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20People's%20suggestions%20to%20the%20contrary%2C%20President%20Trump%20has%20not%20indicated%20that%20he%20will%20assert%20an%20advice-of-counsel%20defense%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20lawyers%2C%20Susan%20Necheles%20and%20Todd%20Blanche%2C%20said%20in%20Thursday's%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20argued%20that%20New%20York%20law%20and%20legal%20precedent%20do%20not%20require%20he%20tip%20his%20hand%2C%20pre-trial%2C%20on%20an%20advice-of-counsel%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EState%20trial-procedure%20laws%20only%20require%20defendants%20to%20give%20advance%20notice%20of%20an%20insanity%20defense%2C%20an%20alibi%20defense%2C%20and%20defenses%20for%20certain%20offenses%20involving%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20provide%20prosecutors%20with%20notice%20of%20his%20intent%20to%20assert%20an%20advice-of-counsel%20defense%20two%20weeks%20before%20the%20March%2025%20trial%20date%2C%20assuming%20Merchan%20rules%20on%20pre-trial%20motions%20by%20March%204%2C%20his%20lawyers%20wrote%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20own%20filing%2C%20prosecutors%20complained%20that%20Trump%20has%20shown%20confusion%20around%20an%20advice-of-counsel%20defense%2C%20at%20one%20point%20last%20month%20naming%20six%20lawyers%20he%20plans%20to%20call%20as%20witnesses%20only%20to%20later%20remove%20them%20from%20his%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20say%20a%20February%2012%20deadline%20would%20give%20them%20the%20necessary%20time%20to%20prepare%20and%20serve%20any%20trial%20subpoenas%20that%20may%20be%20required%20to%20investigate%20Trump's%20blame-the-lawyers%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20note%20that%20%26quot%3BJust%20last%20month%2C%20the%20federal%20court%20presiding%20over%20this%20defendant's%20criminal%20prosecution%20in%20the%20District%20of%20Columbia%20entered%20an%20order%20directing%20defendants%20to%20'provide%20formal%20notice%20whether%20he%20intends%20to%20assert%20an%20advice-o