%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%2017-year-old%20opened%20fire%20at%20an%20Iowa%20high%20school%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20school%20after%20the%20winter%20break.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20sixth-grader%20was%20killed%20and%20five%20others%20were%20wounded.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EVigils%20were%20planned%20Thursday%20evening%20at%20a%20park%20and%20a%20local%20church.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%2017-year-old%20opened%20fire%20at%20a%20small-town%20Iowa%20high%20school%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20school%20after%20the%20winter%20break%2C%20killing%20a%20sixth-grader%20and%20wounding%20five%20others%20Thursday%20as%20students%20barricaded%20in%20offices%2C%20ducked%20into%20classrooms%20and%20fled%20in%20panic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suspect%2C%20a%20student%20at%20the%20school%20in%20Perry%2C%20died%20of%20what%20investigators%20believe%20is%20a%20self-inflicted%20gunshot%20wound%2C%20an%20Iowa%20Division%20of%20Criminal%20Investigation%20official%20said.%20Authorities%20said%20one%20of%20the%20five%20people%20wounded%20was%20an%20administrator%2C%20and%20later%20identified%20as%20Perry%20High%20School%20Principal%20Dan%20Marburger%20by%20an%20eastern%20Iowa%20school%20district%20where%20he%20graduated%20from%20high%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20identified%20the%20shooter%20as%20Dylan%20Butler%2C%2017%2C%20and%20provided%20no%20information%20about%20a%20possible%20motive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerry%20has%20about%208%2C000%20residents%20and%20is%20about%2040%20miles%20(65%20kilometers)%20northwest%20of%20Des%20Moines%2C%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20state%20capital's%20metropolitan%20area.%20It%20is%20home%20to%20a%20large%20pork-processing%20plant%2C%20and%20low-slung%2C%20single-story%20homes%20spread%20among%20trees%20now%20shorn%20of%20their%20leaves%20by%20winter.%20The%20high%20school%20and%20middle%20school%20are%20connected%2C%20sitting%20on%20the%20east%20edge%20of%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20said%20the%20shooter%20had%20a%20pump-action%20shotgun%20and%20a%20small-caliber%20handgun.%20Mitch%20Mortvedt%2C%20the%20state%20investigation%20division's%20assistant%20director%2C%20said%20during%20a%20news%20conference%20that%20authorities%20also%20found%20a%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20rudimentary%26quot%3B%20improvised%20explosive%20device%20and%20rendered%20it%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suspect's%20motive%20is%20being%20investigated%20and%20authorities%20are%20looking%20into%20%26quot%3Ba%20number%20of%20social%20media%20posts%26quot%3B%20he%20made%20around%20the%20time%20of%20the%20shooting%2C%20Mortvedt%20added.%20All%20of%20the%20shootings%20occurred%20inside%20the%20high%20school%2C%20but%20he%20said%20other%20students%20from%20other%20grades%20may%20have%20been%20there%20for%20a%20breakfast%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerry%20High%20School%20senior%20Ava%20Augustus%20said%20she%20was%20awaiting%20a%20counselor%20in%20a%20school%20office%20when%20she%20heard%20three%20shots.%20Unable%20to%20flee%20through%20a%20small%20window%2C%20she%20and%20others%20barricaded%20the%20door%20and%20were%20ready%20to%20throw%20things%20if%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20we%20hear%20'He's%20down.%20You%20can%20go%20out%2C'%26quot%3B%20Augustus%20said%20through%20tears.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20run%20and%20you%20can%20just%20see%20glass%20everywhere%2C%20blood%20on%20the%20floor.%20I%20get%20to%20my%20car%20and%20they're%20taking%20a%20girl%20out%20of%20the%20auditorium%20who%20had%20been%20shot%20in%20her%20leg.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20gunshot%20victims%20were%20taken%20by%20ambulance%20to%20Iowa%20Methodist%20Medical%20Center%20in%20Des%20Moines%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%20Some%20other%20patients%20were%20transported%20to%20a%20second%20hospital%20in%20Des%20Moines%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20MercyOne%20Des%20Moines%20Medical%20Center%20confirmed%2C%20declining%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20number%20of%20patients%20or%20their%20statuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMortvedt%20said%20one%20person%20was%20in%20critical%20condition%20but%20the%20injuries%20did%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20life-threatening.%20The%20other%20victims%20were%20stable%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVigils%20were%20planned%20Thursday%20evening%20at%20a%20park%20and%20a%20local%20church.%20A%20post%20on%20the%20high%20school's%20Facebook%20page%20said%20it%20would%20be%20closed%20Friday%20with%20counseling%20services%20being%20made%20available%20to%20students%20and%20faculty%2C%20and%20others%20in%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGov.%20Kim%20Reynolds%20ordered%20all%20flags%20in%20Iowa%20to%20be%20lowered%20to%20half-staff%20immediately%20on%20Thursday%20and%20to%20remain%20at%20half-staff%20until%20sunset%20on%20Sunday%2C%20in%20support%20of%20the%20community%20and%20the%20school's%20students%2C%20families%2C%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20senseless%20tragedy%20has%20shaken%20our%20entire%20state%20to%20its%20core%2C%26quot%3B%20Reynold%20said%20during%20the%20news%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Washington%2C%20U.S.%20Attorney%20General%20Merrick%20Garland%20was%20briefed%20on%20the%20shooting.%20FBI%20agents%20from%20the%20Omaha-Des%20Moines%20office%20are%20assisting%20with%20the%20investigation%20led%20by%20the%20Iowa%20Division%20of%20Criminal%20Investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shooting%20occurred%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Iowa's%20looming%20first-in-the-nation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fhow-iowa-caucus-works-2024-democrats-republicans-592ab40b9b9b948c0540f2cf132bab5c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresidential%20caucuses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20GOP%20candidate%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20had%20a%20campaign%20event%20scheduled%20in%20Perry%20at%209%20a.m.%20about%201%201%2F2%20miles%20(2.4%20kilometers)%20from%20the%20high%20school%20but%20canceled%20it%20to%20hold%20a%20prayer%20and%20intimate%20discussion%20with%20area%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMass%20shootings%20across%20the%20U.S.%20have%20long%20brought%20calls%20for%20stricter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Fhub%2Fgun-politics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egun%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20gun%20safety%20advocates%2C%20and%20Thursday's%20did%20within%20hours.%20But%20that%20idea%20has%20been%20a%20non-starter%20for%20many%20Republicans%2C%20particularly%20in%20rural%2C%20GOP-leaning%20states%20like%20Iowa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20July%202021%2C%20Iowa%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fia-state-wire-iowa-gun-politics-business-laws-656a5ba4382a64f2d93790f56050ce3c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoes%20not%20require%20a%20permit%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20purchase%20a%20handgun%20or%20carry%20a%20firearm%20in%20public%2C%20though%20it%20mandates%20a%20background%20check%20for%20a%20person%20buying%20a%20handgun%20without%20a%20permit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamaswamy%20said%20the%20shooting%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bpsychological%20sickness%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20country.%20In%20Des%20Moines%2C%20GOP%20rival%20and%20Florida%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%20said%20that%20gun%20violence%20%26quot%3Bis%20more%20of%20a%20local%20and%20state%20issue%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.desmoinesregister.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Felections%2Fpresidential%2Fcaucus%2F2024%2F01%2F04%2Fafter-iowa-school-shooting-ron-desantis-pitches-no-new-gun-restrictions%2F72107293007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Des%20Moines%20Register%20and%20NBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20school%20in%20Perry%20is%20part%20of%20the%201%2C785-student%20Perry%20Community%20School%20District.%20The%20town%20is%20more%20diverse%20than%20Iowa%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20with%20census%20figures%20showing%20that%2031%25%20of%20the%20residents%20are%20Hispanic%2C%20compared%20to%20less%20than%207%25%20for%20the%20state.%20Those%20figures%20also%20show%20that%20nearly%2019%25%20of%20the%20town's%20residents%20were%20born%20outside%20the%20U.S.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20said%20an%20active%20shooter%20was%20reported%20at%207%3A37%20a.m.%20Thursday%20and%20officers%20arrived%20within%20minutes.%20Emergency%20vehicles%20surrounded%20the%20middle%20and%20high%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOfficers%20immediately%20attempted%20to%20locate%20the%20source%20of%20the%20threat%20and%20quickly%20found%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20the%20shooter%20with%20a%20self-inflicted%20gunshot%20wound%2C%26quot%3B%20Mortvedt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZander%20Shelley%2C%2015%2C%20was%20in%20a%20hallway%20when%20he%20heard%20gunshots%20and%20dashed%20into%20a%20classroom%2C%20according%20to%20his%20father%2C%20Kevin%20Shelley.%20Zander%20was%20grazed%20twice%20and%20hid%20in%20the%20classroom%20before%20texting%20his%20father%20at%207%3A36%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%20Shelley%2C%20who%20drives%20a%20garbage%20truck%2C%20told%20his%20boss%20he%20had%20to%20run.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20most%20scared%20I've%20been%20in%20my%20entire%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20posted%20a%20photo%20on%20Facebook%20of%20his%20son%20being%20treated%20at%20the%20Methodist%20Medical%20Center%20and%20said%20the%20boy%20was%20feeling%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20still%20shaking%20and%20tho%20I%20dont%20show%20it%20I'm%20not%20ok.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERachael%20Kares%2C%20an%2018-year-old%20senior%2C%20was%20wrapping%20up%20jazz%20band%20practice%20when%20she%20and%20her%20bandmates%20heard%20what%20she%20described%20as%20four%20gunshots%2C%20spaced%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20just%20jumped%2C%26quot%3B%20Kares%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20band%20teacher%20looked%20at%20us%20and%20yelled%2C%20'Run!'%20So%20we%20ran.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKares%20and%20many%20others%20from%20the%20school%20ran%20out%20past%20the%20football%20field%2C%20as%20she%20heard%20people%20yelling%2C%20%26quot%3BGet%20out!%20Get%20out!%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20she%20heard%20additional%20shots%20as%20sh