esidents%20and%20legislative%20party%20leaders%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Thursday%2C%20in%20which%20discussions%20on%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20were%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20September%202022%20to%20January%202023%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%204000-km%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20from%20Kashmir%20to%20Kanyakumari%20was%20a%20transformative%20%3Cem%3Epadyatra%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20changed%20Indian%20politics%20and%20energised%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20enthused%20the%20party%20cadre%20across%20different%20states.%20The%20yatra%20was%20a%20milestone%20in%20our%20party%E2%80%99s%20history%20as%20well%20as%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20issues%20raised%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20economy%2C%20political%20justice%2C%20and%20authoritarianism%20across%2012%20states%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20were%20discussed%20at%20today%E2%80%99s%20meeting.%20The%20message%20of%20that%20yatra%20was%20emphasised%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20by%20Kharge%20and%20all%20our%20leaders.%20On%20the%20basis%20of%20all%20suggestions%20that%20were%20received%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20today%20that%20this%20yatra%20should%20be%20renamed%20as%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%20In%20the%20Preamble%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%2C%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20political%20justice%20is%20mentioned.%20Equality%2C%20liberty%2C%20justice%2C%20and%20fraternity%20are%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Preamble.%20It%20was%20unanimously%20agreed%20that%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20on%20our%20organisation%20and%20Indian%20politics%20should%20not%20be%20forgotten%20and%20instead%20taken%20forward%20and%20therefore%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20rename%20this%20yatra%20as%20justice%20is%20our%20goal%20%E2%80%93%20economic%2C%20social%20and%20political%20justice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20previous%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20this%20one%20will%20mostly%20be%20conducted%20by%20bus%2C%20but%20it%20will%20also%20include%20walks%20by%20Gandhi%20during%20which%20he%20will%20meet%20people%20and%20civil%20society%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20speculation%20around%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20losing%20steam%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20with%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20yet%20to%20be%20finalised%2C%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20everyone%20is%20invited%20to%20the%20yatra%2C%20including%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20say%20that%20everyone%20is%20invited%20to%20this%20yatra.%20Our%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%2C%20other%20parties%20who%20are%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%20different%20states%20as%20well%20civil%20society%20organisations%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20we%20invite%20them%20to%20join%20our%20yatra.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Congress%20leaders%20will%20hold%20discussions%20with%20INDIA%20alliance%20members%20for%20them%20to%20join%20the%20yatra%20at%20any%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20meeting%20is%20also%20scheduled%20for%20Thursday%20evening%20when%20Kharge%20will%20meet%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Congress%20National%20Alliance%20Committee%20that%20includes%20Mukul%20Wasnik%2C%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20Salman%20Khurshid%2C%20Mohan%20Prakash%2C%20to%20discuss%20details%20of%20the%20alliances%20in%20different%20states%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20met%20our%20party%20leaders%20in%20all%20states%20and%20after%20their%20meeting%20with%20Kharge%2C%20future%20meetings%20with%20different%20parties%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20be%20decided%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704376650000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F02122433%2Fimage-687.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpo