n%20misled%20when%20the%20conference%20decided%20to%20rename%20%E2%80%98Chin%20State%E2%80%99%20as%20%E2%80%98Chinland%2C%E2%80%99%20raising%20concerns%20over%20whether%20it%20will%20opt%20for%20independence.%20The%20constitution%20explicitly%20calls%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20federal%20union%20which%20enshrines%20full%20self-determination%2C%20equal%20political%20rights%2C%20and%20national%20rights%20for%20the%20Chin.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Chinland%20Council%20seeks%20self-determination%20and%20sovereignty%20over%20its%20area%20rather%20than%20declaring%20itself%20to%20be%20an%20independent%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20meeting%20minutes%2C%20the%20Chinland%20Council%20has%20a%20mandate%20to%20set%20up%20the%20Chinland%20government%2C%20which%20consists%20of%20a%20parliament%2C%20cabinet%2C%20and%20supreme%20court%2C%20within%2060%20days.%20As%20the%20constitution%20stipulates%2C%20the%20Chinland%20Council%20has%20a%20mandate%20to%20oversee%20the%20effective%20operation%20of%20these%20fundamental%20institutions%20and%20the%20current%20CNF%20chairman%2C%20Pu%20Zing%20Cung%2C%20will%20chair%20the%20Council%20for%20two%20years.%20The%20constitution%20will%20serve%20as%20the%20first%20ever%20Chin%20State%20constitution%20enacted%20by%20the%20Chin%20for%20the%20Chin%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20establishment%20of%20the%20Chinland%20Council%20meanwhile%20abolishes%20the%20Chinland%20Joint%20Defense%20Committee%20(CJDC)%2C%20a%20coalition%20of%20pro-democracy%20armed%20groups%20formed%20after%20the%20coup.%20From%20loosely%20collaboration%20previously%2C%20Chin%20State%20is%20expected%20to%20see%20a%20stronger%20command-and-control%20system%20under%20the%20new%20defense%20ministry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPolitical%20implications%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Chinland%20Council%2C%20I%20expect%20to%20see%20formulating%20a%20well-coordinated%20and%20comprehensive%20policy%20toward%20alliances%20and%20international%20relations%20under%20the%20new%20government.%20This%20approach%20should%20include%20determining%20how%20to%20collaborate%20or%20adopt%20a%20parallel%20approach%20in%20working%20alongside%20the%20National%20Unity%20Government.%20Now%2C%20having%20approximately%2060%2C000%20of%20internally%20displaced%20peoples%20(IDPs)%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20militarisation%20and%20cyclone%20mocha%2C%20cross-border%20aid%20could%20be%20something%20the%20international%20community%20should%20engage%20with%20the%20Council%20through%20the%20Indian%20Govt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20recent%20political%20development%20in%20Chin%20State%20draws%20India%20attention%2C%20to%20address%20its%20interests%20in%20border%20security%2C%20counterbalancing%20China%E2%80%99s%20influence%2C%20and%20effectively%20managing%20its%20major%20business%20ventures%20in%20Myanmar.%20Of%20particular%20concern%20are%20connectivity%20projects%20like%20India%E2%80%99s%20Kaladan%20Multimodal%20Transit%20Transport%20and%20the%20India-Myanmar-Thailand%20trilateral%20highway%20project%2C%20which%20are%20set%20to%20traverse%20Chin%20State.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChin-Mizo%20Relations%20Amid%20Border%20Issues%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20recent%20Mizoram%20state%E2%80%99s%20election%20has%20marked%20another%20milestone%20for%20Indo-Myanmar%20relations.%20Though%20we%20do%20not%20expect%20to%20see%20a%20different%20Mizo%20State%E2%80%99s%20refugee%20policy%20under%20the%20new%20Zoram%20People%20Movement%20(ZPM)%20party%2C%20the%20newly%20appointed%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Mizoram%2C%20Lalduhoma%2C%20keen%20to%20maintain%20a%20good%20relationship%20with%20the%20Chin.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20publicly%20supports%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Freporter-vlogs%2Fwill-lalduhoma-and-his-young-party-zpm-be-king-or-kingmaker-in-mizoram-polls-736592%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereunification%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20Zo%20communities%20(Chin-Kuki-Mizo)%20and%20expresses%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Chin%20people%20in%20Myanmar%20and%20Kuki%20in%20Manipur%20state%2C%20emphasising%20their%20interconnectedness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20This%20robust%20backing%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20reminder%20to%20the%20Chin%20community%20of%20the%20significance%20of%20fortifying%20their%20ties%20to%20the%20Mizoram%20government%20and%20Mizo%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistorically%2C%20the%20Chin%20and%20Mizo%20communities%20have%20shared%20a%20great%20bond%3B%20the%20Mizo%20community%20warmly%20welcome%20and%20generously%20support%20the%20Chin%2C%20offering%20shelter%2C%20food%2C%20and%20unwavering%20assistance%20in%20sharing%20the%20burdens%20faced%20by%20the%20Chin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp-300x198.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp-1024x675.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-628160%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22791%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20image%3A%20A%20Zawlsei%20refugee%20camp%20in%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20Aizawl.%20The%20camp%20serves%20as%20home%20to%20Myanmarese%20who%20fled%20the%20military%20persecution%20in%20their%20country.%20Photo%3A%20Sushila%20Sahay%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20tie%20between%20the%20two%20communities%2C%20illicit%20drugs%20have%20been%20a%20major%20concern.%20The%20vice-president%20of%20the%20sub-headquarter%20YMA%20Champhai%2C%20a%20prominent%20youth%20organisation%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fzalen.info%2Fvideos%2F7587529004608064%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehighlighted%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20a%20recent%20report%20the%20significant%20worry%20among%20the%20Mizo%20community%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eregarding%20the%20influx%20of%20illicit%20drugs%20across%20borders.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20Chinland%20government%20also%20has%20to%20make%20an%20impression%20on%20the%20Mizoram%20government%20and%20its%20people%20who%20have%20been%20long%20supporting%20the%20Chin%20people%20as%20well%20as%20New%20Delhi%20with%20regards%20to%20illegal%20drugs%20and%20crimes%20that%20fall%20within%20its%20purview.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20a%20recent%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unodc.org%2Froseap%2Fen%2F2023%2F12%2Fsoutheast-asia-opium-survey-report-launch%2Fstory.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUNODC%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20opium%20cultivation%20in%20Chin%20State%20has%20surged%20by%2010%25%20following%20the%20coup.%20This%20significant%20increase%20poses%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20both%20India%20and%20the%20Chin%20community%2C%20necessitating%20urgent%20attention%20and%20action%20to%20curb%20its%20growth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20sharing%20the%20same%20bloodline%20or%20kinship%2C%20the%20geographic%20separation%20takes%20the%20relationship%20into%20account.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20Chin%20has%20to%20establish%20positive%20ties%20with%20the%20Mizoram%20administration%2C%20which%20offers%20individuals%20seeking%20asylum%20in%20the%20region%20access%20to%20healthcare%20and%20education.%20Importantly%2C%20the%20Chin%20has%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20refugee%20issues%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20resettlement%20and%20rehabilitation%20sectors.%20In%20that%20regard%2C%20both%20parties%20must%20be%20concerned%20about%20crossing%20borders%20through%20a%20coordinating%20organisation%2C%20for%20instance%20a%20local%20border%20security%20coordination%20committee%20or%20refugee%20coordination%20committee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOverall%2C%20India%20stands%20at%20a%20critical%20juncture%20in%20its%20relations%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20evolving%20landscape%20of%20the%20Chin%20resistance%20forces%20and%20the%20weakening%20junta.%20The%20establishment%20of%20the%20Chinland%20Council%2C%20coupled%20with%20political%20changes%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20demands%20a%20cautious%20diplomatic%20strategy%20by%20India%20to%20secure%20its%20interests%20while%20navigating%20the%20complexities%20of%20the%20region.%20Given%20that%20Naypyidaw%20has%20lost%20significant%20territorial%20control%2C%20particularly%20since%20the%201027%20operation%2C%20New%20Delhi%20should%20not%20be%20putting%20all%20of%20its%20resources%20behind%20the%20military%20dictatorship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESalai%20Van%20Bawi%20Mang%2C%20a%20Chin%20ethnic%20researcher%20from%20Chin%20State%2C%20explores%20Indo-Myanmar%20relations%20and%20governance%2C%20dedicating%20his%20efforts%20to%20advancing%20democracy%2C%20peace%2C%20and%20federalism%20within%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704357054000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04131744%2FScreenshot-2024-01-04-at-1.15.12-e1704354518745.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fchin-state-operation-1027-myanmar-mizoram%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20establishment%20of%20the%20Chinland%20Council%2C%20coupled%20with%20political%20changes%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20demands%20a%20cautious%20diplomatic%20strategy%20by%20India%20to%20secure%20its%20interests%20while%20navigating%20the%20complexities%20of%20the%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fchin-state-operation-1027-myanmar-mizoram%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22YS%20Sharmila%20Joins%20Congress%2C%20Likely%20to%20Boost%20Party's%20Prospects%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04135456%2FEffect-54.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Buoyed%20by%20its%20recent%20victory%20in%20the%20Telangana%20Assembly%20elections%20and%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20revive%20its%20fortunes%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20which%20goes%20to%20the%20polls%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Congress%20on%20Thursday%20inducted%20Y.S.%20Sharmila%20into%20the%20party%20in%20New%20Delhi%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20former%20party%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20induction%20into%20the%20grand%20old%20party%2C%20Sharmila%20announced%20the%20merger%20of%20her%20Yuvajana%20Sramika%20Rythu%20(YSR)%20Telangana%20Party%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20gives%20me%20immense%20joy%20that%20the%20YSR%20Telangana%20Party%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20from%20today%20onwards%2C%20that%20YSR%20Telangana%20Party%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20separate%20anymore%20from%20the%20Congress%20party%20gives%20me%20great%20delight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharmila%20said%20while%20addressing%20reporters%20after%20her%20induction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmila%20launched%20the%20YSR%20Telangana%20Party%20in%20July%202021%20after%20serious%20differences%20arose%20between%20her%20and%20her%20brother%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20and%20YSRCP%20chief%20Y.S%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20father%20and%20veteran%20Congress%20leader%20Y.S.%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%20led%20the%20party%20to%20victory%20in%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20twice%20in%202004%20and%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmila%20said%20that%20her%20father%20would%20be%20happy%20with%20his%20daughter%20returning%20to%20the%20Congress%20fold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CY%20S%20Rajashekhar%20Reddy%2C%20the%20legendary%20leader%20of%20the%20Telugu%20people%20not%20only%20served%20the%20Congress%20party%20all%20his%20life%20but%20also%20gave%20his%20life%20serving%20the%20Congress%20party.%20And%20today%20it%20would%20give%20him%20great%20joy%20that%20his%20daughter%20is%20following%20in%20his%20footsteps%20and%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04140021%2FEffect-55.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04140021%2FEffect-55.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04140021%2FEffect-55-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04140021%2FEffect-55-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691618%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EY.S.%20Sharmila%20with%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Largest%20secular%20party%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Congress%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Clargest%20secular%20party%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Sharmila%20said%20that%20her%20decision%20to%20join%20the%20party%20was%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20ongoing%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20party%20is%20still%20the%20largest%20secular%20party%20of%20our%20country.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20always%20upheld%20the%20true%20culture%20of%20India.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20built%20our%20nation%E2%80%99s%20foundations%20up.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20unwaveringly%20served%20all%20communities%2C%20uniting%20all%20sections%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20must%20also%20say%20at%20this%20moment%20that%20as%20a%20Christian%20it%20pained%20that%20such%20cruelty%20took%20place%20in%20Manipur.%202%2C000%20churches%20were%20vandalised%2C%20and%2060%2C000%20people%20became%20homeless.%20And%20that%20kind%20of%20cruelty%20is%20something%20I%20am%20not%20able%20to%20digest%20till%20this%20day.%20That%20is%20the%20day%20I%20thought%2C%20it%20suddenly%20struck%20me%20that%20this%20is%20what%20will%20happen%20if%20a%20secular%20party%20is%20not%20in%20power.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20am%20joining%20the%20Congress%20and%20merging%20the%20YSR%20Telangana%20Party%20with%20it%20today%20very%20gladly%20because%20I%20know%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20will%20uphold%20all%20the%20sections%20of%20the%20people%20in%20Indian%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsharmilas-ysr-party-wont-contest-telangana-assembly-polls-offers-support-to-congress%5C%22%3ESharmila%E2%80%99s%20YSR%20Party%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Contest%20Telangana%20Assembly%20Polls%2C%20Offers%20Support%20to%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%E2%80%99%20revival%20plans%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmila%E2%80%99s%20induction%20into%20the%20Congress%20comes%20as%20the%20party%20looks%20to%20revive%20its%20fortunes%20in%20the%20state%20ahead%20of%20Assembly%20elections%20and%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20the%20party%20appointed%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Manickam%20Tagore%20B%20(who%20had%20earlier%20served%20as%20the%20AICC%20in-charge%20in%20Telangana)%20as%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20party%20in-charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20induction%20comes%20just%20a%20week%20after%20a%20strategy%20meeting%20of%20Andhra%20leaders%20in%20Delhi%20under%20Kharge%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20on%20December%2027%2C%20after%20which%20Tagore%20wrote%20on%20X%20that%20the%20party%20welcomes%20all%20those%20who%20have%20left%20the%20organisation%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20to%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20welcome%20the%20leaders%20and%20workers%20who%20have%20left%20Congress%20in%20Andhra%20and%20believe%20in%20the%20ideology%20of%20Congress%20to%20come%20back%20and%20contribute%20to%20building%20a%20better%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe%20welcome%20the%20leaders%20and%20workers%20who%20have%20left%20Congress%20in%20Andhra%20and%20believe%20in%20the%20ideology%20of%20Congress%20to%20come%20back%20and%20contribute%20to%20building%20a%20better%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FComeBackToCongress%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ComeBackToCongress%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINC_Andhra%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40INC_Andhra%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Manickam%20Tagore%20.B%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%E0%AE%AE%E0%AE%BE%E0%AE%A3%E0%AE%BF%E0%AE%95%E0%AF%8D%E0%AE%95%E0%AE%AE%E0%AF%8D%20%E0%AE%A4%E0%AE%BE%E0%AE%95%E0%AF%82%E0%AE%B0%E0%AF%8D.%E0%AE%AA%20(%40manickamtagore)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanickamtagore%2Fstatus%2F1739989892309156071%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20meeting%20Kharge%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cevery%20leader%20and%20worker%20is%20going%20to%20work%20hard%20and%20reestablish%20the%20bond%20which%20the%20people%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20once%20shared%20with%20the%20Congress%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmila%20shot%20to%20prominence%20when%20she%20undertook%20a%203%2C100%20km%20padayatra%20in%20erstwhile%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20when%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20was%20in%20jail%20in%20a%20disproportionate%20assets%20case%20in%202012-13.%20She%20had%20also%20campaigned%20for%20her%20brother%20in%20his%20absence%20while%20he%20was%20in%20jail%20in%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20byelections%20which%20then%20led%20the%20YSRCP%20to%20win%2015%20out%20of%2018%20Assembly%20constituencies%20and%20Nellore%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20that%20went%20to%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20brother%E2%80%99s%20release%20from%20jail%2C%20Sharmila%20again%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20victory%20of%20the%20YSRCP%20in%20elections%20to%20the%202019%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20elections%20which%20ended%20the%20TDP%20rule%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20differences%20with%20her%20brother%2C%20Sharmila%20took%20out%20another%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fysrtpchief-sharmila-announces-padayatra-from-october-20-101632250454746.html%5C%22%3E%20padyatra%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Telangana.%20It%20was%20reported%20that%20she%20had%20political%20ambitions%20but%20in%20Telangana%20and%20not%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%20in%20Telangana%2C%20she%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsharmilas-ysr-party-wont-contest-telangana-assembly-polls-offers-support-to-congress%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20her%20party%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20the%20Congress%20by%20deciding%20to%20not%20contest%20the%20polls.%20Following%20her%20induction%2C%20she%20said%20that%20she%20is%20happy%20to%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20election%20victory%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMr.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20gained%20immense%20confidence%20not%20only%20in%20me%20but%20most%20people%20in%20India%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra.%20And%20that%20yatra%20led%20to%20the%20victory%20in%20Karnataka.%20I%20realised%20that%20will%20have%20a%20domino%20effect%20in%20Telangana%20and%20therefore%2C%20because%20Congress%20stood%20a%20chance%20of%20winning%20in%20Telangana%2C%20I%20graciously%20withheld%20from%20contesting%20the%20elections%20in%20Telangana%20because%20we%20did%20not%20want%20to%20break%20the%20anti-KCR%20vote%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20Congress%20has%20won%20in%20the%20state%20and%20I%20am%20most%20happy%20that%20we%20contributed%20to%20that%20victory.%20It%20was%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20dream%20to%20see%20Mr.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20our%20country%20and%20I%20am%20very%20glad%20that%20I%20am%20going%20to%20be%20a%20part%20in%20making%20that%20happen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20has%20not%20yet%20announced%20what%20role%20will%20be%20given%20to%20Sharmila%2C%20she%20said%20that%20she%20will%20serve%20the%20party%20in%20%E2%80%9Cwhichever%20responsibility%20with%20loyalty%2C%20dignity%20and%20diligence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20meets%20KCR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20his%20sister%20joined%20the%20Congress%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20called%20on%20former%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Hyderabad.%20Earlier%20on%20Wednesday%20while%20addressing%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Kakinada%2C%20Jagan%20accused%20opposition%20parties%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdividing%20families%E2%80%9D%20and%20forming%20unholy%20alliances.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20coming%20days%20will%20see%20an%20%E2%80%9Cincrease%20in%20party%20alliances%20which%20will%20break%20apart%20families%20and%20even%20bring%20about%20atrocities%2C%20false%20promises%20and%20pave%20way%20for%20deceit%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Fopposition-attempting-to-break-families-for-political-gains-ap-cm-jagan-reddy%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Fopposition-attempting-to-break-families-for-political-gains-ap-cm-jagan-reddy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704356559000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04135456%2FEffect-54.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fys-sharmila-joins-congress-likely-to-boost-partys-prospects-in-andhra-pradesh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Calling%20it%20the%20'largest%20secular%20party%2C%20Sharmila%20said%20that%20her%20decision%20to%20join%20the%20Congress%20was%20spurred%20by%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20that%20she%20had%20'contributed'%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20victory%20in%20Telangana%20Assembly%20elections%20last%20year%20by%20not%20contesting%20the%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fys-sharmila-joins-congress-likely-to-boost-partys-prospects-in-andhra-pradesh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Companies%20Fail%20But%20Promoters%20Don%E2%80%99t%3A%20The%20NCLT's%20Continuing%20Tradition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04122517%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Company%20Law%20Tribunal%2C%20which%20was%20seen%20as%20one%20of%20the%20major%20reforms%20to%20tackle%20bad%20loan%20recovery%2C%20has%20turned%20five%20amid%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20efficiency%20of%20its%20process%20and%20its%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Corporate%20Insolvency%20Resolution%20Process%20determines%20whether%20a%20defaulter%20can%20repay%20or%20not%2C%20by%20evaluating%20assets%20and%20liabilities.%20If%20a%20corporate%20becomes%20insolvent%2C%20a%20financial%20creditor%20(bank%2Fnon-bank%20financial%20company)%20an%20operational%20creditor%20(supplier%2Fcontractor%20etc.)%2C%20or%20the%20defaulting%20corporate%20itself%20may%20initiate%20CIRP%20by%20filing%20an%20application%20with%20the%20NCLT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCLT%20is%20an%20adjudicating%20authority%20responsible%20for%20resolving%20disputes%20related%20to%20company%20law%2C%20mergers%2C%20amalgamations%20and%20the%20winding%20up%20of%20companies%20%E2%80%95%20the%20insolvency%20resolution%20process%20of%20companies%20and%20limited%20liability%20partnerships%20under%20the%20Insolvency%20and%20Bankruptcy%20Code%2C%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResolution%20professionals%20submit%20a%20resolution%20plan%20as%20approved%20by%20the%20committee%20of%20creditors%20to%20the%20NCLT.%20The%20Committee%20of%20Creditors%20(CoC)%20may%20approve%20it%20with%20at%20least%2066%25%20voting%20for%20it.%20The%20plan%20becomes%20binding%20on%20the%20corporate%20debtor%2C%20its%20employees%2C%20members%2C%20creditors%2C%20guarantors%20and%20other%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fe1e33d90-9626-428a-8f15-74a031831af3%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fe1e33d90-9626-428a-8f15-74a031831af3%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1704422178567000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1BWqI_Wu0ygIBeJAncHTta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fe1e33d90-9626-428a-8f15-74a031831af3%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fe1e33d90-9626-428a-8f15-74a031831af3%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1704422178567000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1BWqI_Wu0ygIBeJAncHTta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0news%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20headlined%3A%20%E2%80%98NCLT%20Mumbai%20approves%20resolution%20plan%20for%20Reliance%20Communications%20Infrastructure%20Ltd%2C%20valued%20at%20Rs%20455.9%20crore%20as%20against%20total%20admitted%20claim%20of%20Rs%2047%2C251%20crores.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20group%20company%20had%20a%20debt%20of%20Rs%2046%2C000%20crore%2C%20with%2053%20financial%20creditors%20%E2%80%94%20including%20local%20and%20foreign%20banks%2C%20NBFCs%20and%20funds%20%E2%80%94%20laying%20claims.%20The%20NCLT%E2%80%99s%20Mumbai%20Bench%20on%20December%2019%20approved%20a%20resolution%20plan%20for%20RCIL%2C%20a%20wholly%20owned%20subsidiary%20of%20Reliance%20Communications%20Limited%20(RCOM).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETotal%20claims%20made%20by%20debtors%3A%20Rs%204%2C96%2C68%2C01%2C09%2C556%20(Rs%2049%2C668%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETotal%20claims%20admitted%20by%20NCLT%3A%20Rs%204%2C72%2C51%2C34%2C03%2C502%20(Rs%2047%2C251%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCLT%20has%20approved%20a%20plan%20by%20which%20the%20Anil%20Ambani%20Group%20has%20to%20pay%20just%200.92%25%20of%20their%20debts%20%E2%80%95%20only%20Rs%20455.92%20crore%20of%20the%20Rs%2049%2C668%20crore%20claimed.%20The%20remaining%20Rs%2049%2C212.08%20crore%20will%C2%A0%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0be%20paid%20back%20by%20Anil%20Ambani%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20directly%20lent%20amount%20of%20Rs%20182.20%20crore%20that%20this%20group%20availed%2C%20the%20balance%20dues%20admitted%20were%20corporate%20guarantees%20and%20other%20or%20similar%20third-party%20obligations%20of%20the%20debtor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20corporate%20guarantee%20is%20an%20agreement%20in%20which%20one%20party%2C%20the%20guarantor%2C%20takes%20on%20the%20payments%20or%20responsibilities%20of%20a%20debt%20if%20the%20debtor%20defaults.%20This%20is%20often%20used%20when%20one%20of%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20sister%20(or%20brother)%20companies%20seek%20funds%20from%20a%20financial%20institution.%20Mostly%2C%20governments%20are%20customers%20for%20infrastructure%20projects.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20performance%20or%20bank%20guarantees%2C%20there%20is%20no%20coverage%20of%20risk%20owing%20to%20non-performance%20of%20the%20developer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Filfs-downfall-banking-india-economy%5C%22%3Edemise%20of%20IL%26amp%3BFS%20four%20years%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20financial%20crises%20caused%20by%20a%20major%20conglomerate%2C%20seizing%20up%20the%20financial%20system%20and%20exhausting%20liquidity.%20The%20debt%20involved%20was%20over%20Rs%201%20lakh%20crore%2C%20of%20which%20only%20Rs%2055%2C000%20crore%20was%20addressed%2C%20leaving%2062%25%20unresolved.%20LIC%2C%20SBI%2C%20HDFC%20and%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20Orix%20Corp%20are%20some%20of%20the%20key%20stakeholders%20of%20this%20NBFC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20consider%20another%20classic%20example%20in%20which%20NCLT%20could%20not%20protect%20the%20creditors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELenders%20to%20debt-ridden%20Videocon%20Industries%20agreed%20to%20take%20a%20haircut%20of%20nearly%2096%25%2C%20the%20NCLT%20has%20observed%20while%20approving%20the%20Vedanta%20group%E2%80%99s%20Twin%20Star%20Technologies%20bid%20for%20it.%20The%20claims%20admitted%20were%20for%20Rs%2064%2C838.63%20crore%20and%20the%20resolution%20plan%20was%20approved%20for%20Rs%202%2C962.02%20crore%20%E2%80%95%20just%204.15%25%20of%20the%20claim%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20case%20of%20bankrupt%20and%20grounded%20Jet%20Airways%2C%20where%20the%20resolution%20%E2%80%94%20in%20favour%20of%20new%20buyers%2C%20UK-headquartered%20Kalrock%20Capital%20and%20UAE-based%20Murari%20Lal%20Jalan%20%E2%80%94%20has%20taken%20over%20two%20years.%20The%20Kalrock-Jalan%20combine%20has%20agreed%20to%20pay%20financial%20creditors%20just%20Rs%201%2C183%20crore%20(7.86%25)%20over%20five%20years%2C%20against%20admitted%20claims%20of%20over%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCLT%E2%80%99s%20performance%20can%20be%20measured%20with%20two%20different%20matrices%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERecovery%20rate%20(what%20banks%20and%20other%20financial%20institutions%20recover%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20amounts%20claimed)%20and%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAverage%20time%20taken%20by%20the%20resolution%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20deeper%20look%20at%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20NCLT%20reveals%20a%20range%20of%20problems.%C2%A0Admission%20of%20cases%20often%20takes%206-12%20months%20and%20there%20are%20delays%20in%20releasing%20tribunal%20orders.%20Creditors%20file%20multiple%20applications%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lack%20of%20consensus%20within%20the%20committee%20of%20creditors%20and%20too%20few%20NCLT%20judges%20to%20hear%20cases%2C%20which%20results%20in%20the%20pressure%20of%20multiple%20jurisdictions%2C%20and%20delay%20in%20infusion%20of%20funds%20by%20investors%20as%20envisaged%20by%20the%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20348%20cases%20resolved%20in%20NCLT%20as%20of%20March%202021%2C%20the%20average%20time%20for%20resolution%2C%20including%20litigation%20time%2C%20was%20459%20days.%20This%20is%20way%20beyond%20the%20revised%20time%20limit%20of%20330%20days%20prescribed%20by%20the%20government%20in%20July%202019.%20Prior%20to%20this%2C%20the%20expected%20timeframe%20for%20a%20resolution%20was%20270%20days.%20At%20the%20current%20pace%20of%20disposal%20of%20cases%2C%20the%20backlog%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20cleared%20in%204-5%20years.%C2%A0Why%20is%20the%20discipline%20of%20the%20law%20not%20being%20adhered%20to%20in%20full%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20on%20December%2031%2C%202022%2C%20NCLT%20had%20looked%20into%20admitted%20claims%20of%20Rs%207.91%20lakh%20crore%20lent%20by%20banks%20and%20financial%20institutions%20to%20corporates.%20Banks%20have%20written%20off%20bad%20loans%20worth%20Rs%2014.56%20lakh%20crore%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20financial%20years%2C%20from%202014-15.%20Written%20off%20loans%20to%20industries%20and%20services%20stood%20at%20Rs%207.40%20lakh%20crore.%20Only%20a%20minuscule%20amount%20from%20this%20is%20recovered%20by%20banks.%20The%20remaining%20default%20amount%20has%20to%20be%20paid%20off%20from%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20own%20capital%20or%20its%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20holds%20more%20than%2051%25%20of%20shares%20in%20public%20sector%20banks.%20Market%20capitalisation%20of%20the%20top%2010%20banks%20in%20India%20is%20over%20Rs%2036%20lakh%20crore.%20There%20is%20still%20enough%20left%20there%20to%20be%20looted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20too%20long%2C%20India%20has%20seen%20a%20corporate%20history%20where%20companies%20have%20failed%20but%20promoters%20have%20not.%20The%C2%A0promoters%20cannot%C2%A0and%20should%20not%20have%20a%20free%20ride%20or%20continue%20to%20master%20control%20over%20their%20company%20fraudulently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPaul%20Koshy%20is%20a%20consultant%20in%20infrastructure%20development%20and%20engineering.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704355229000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04122517%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcompanies-fail-but-promoters-dont-the-nclts-continuing-tradition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%C2%A0promoters%20cannot%C2%A0and%20should%20not%20have%20a%20free%20ride%20or%20continue%20to%20master%20control%20over%20their%20company%20fraudulently.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcompanies-fail-but-promoters-dont-the-nclts-continuing-tradition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20Unending%20Employment%20Woes%3A%20Over%2025%2C000%20Applicants%20for%2015%20Government%20Posts%20in%20Karnataka%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25133033%2Fimage-1429.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Over%2025%2C000%20individuals%20are%20set%20to%20take%20exams%20on%20January%206%20and%207%20for%20just%2015%20superintendent%20posts%20in%20the%20commercial%20taxes%20department%20in%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20Kalyana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20there%20is%20a%20large%20number%20of%20vacancies%2C%20a%20substantial%20number%20remain%20unfilled%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20huge%20rush%20for%20every%20recruitment%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Fkarnataka%2F2024%2Fjan%2F04%2F25k-aspirants-for-15-posts-rush-for-government-jobs-upi