versy%20over%20the%20cost%20of%20selfie%20points%20with%20Prime%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20image%20installed%20at%20railway%20stations%2C%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20has%20tightened%20norms%20for%20Zonal%20Railways%20furnishing%20information%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act.%20As%20per%20the%20changed%20rules%2C%20all%20RTI%20replies%20must%20go%20through%20general%20managers%20of%20zonal%20railways%20or%20divisional%20railway%20managers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railway%20Board%2C%20in%20an%20advisory%20sent%20out%20to%20general%20managers%2C%20on%20December%2028%2C%202023%2C%20said%20it%20had%20come%20to%20its%20notice%20that%20lately%20%E2%80%9Cquality%20of%20replies%20to%20RTI%20applications%20handled%20by%20Zonal%20Railways%20and%20other%20field%20units%20had%20deteriorated%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Feditorial%2Fstriking-fear-on-hit-and-run-accident-cases-and-section-106-of-the-bharatiya-nyaya-sanhita%2Farticle67703190.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTimelines%20for%20disposal%20of%20RTI%20applications%20were%20surpassed%20in%20many%20cases%20resulting%20in%20a%20large%20number%20of%20appeals%20filed%20before%20the%20First%20Appellate%20Authority%20or%20the%20Central%20Information%20Commission%2C%20not%20only%20increasing%20the%20quantum%20of%20work%20but%20bringing%20disrepute%20to%20the%20organisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20advisory%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tide%20over%20these%20problems%2C%20the%20advisory%20said%20a%20decision%20had%20been%20made%20that%20timelines%20for%20disposal%20prescribed%20in%20the%20Act%20should%20be%20complied%20with%20at%20any%20cost.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20also%20said%20to%20ensure%20quality%2C%20all%20RTI%20replies%20going%20forward%20must%20be%20approved%20respectively%20at%20the%20level%20of%20the%20general%20manager%20(GM)%20in%20Zonal%20Railways%20and%20divisional%20railway%20managers%20(DRMs)%20in%20the%20Divisions.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CSimilarly%2C%20replies%20to%20first%20appeals%20received%20under%20the%20RTI%20Act%20need%20to%20be%20shown%20to%20the%20GM%20and%20DRM%20concerned%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20advisory%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20Railways%20had%20Public%20Information%20Officer%20and%20Chief%20Public%20Information%20Officer%20under%20provisions%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%2C%202005%2C%20to%20furnish%20information%20sought%20by%20petitioners.%20Neither%20general%20managers%20nor%20divisional%20railway%20managers%20had%20any%20role%20to%20play%20as%20appellate%20or%20competent%20authority%20as%20per%20the%20Act%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20quoting%20sources%20in%20the%20Southern%20Railway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20changes%20have%20been%20brought%20into%20force%20after%20it%20came%20to%20light%20that%20each%20permanent%20selfie%20booth%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20image%20costs%20Rs%206.25%20lakh%20while%20each%20temporary%20selfie%20booth%20costs%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%2C%20which%20is%20the%20approved%20cost%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Communication%20under%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting.%20The%20above%20information%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20furnished%20by%20the%20Central%20Railway%20in%20response%20to%20an%20RTI%20query.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20further%20deepened%20after%20the%20authorities%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcentral-railways-pro-transferred-without-notice-after-releasing-costs-of-modi-selfie-points%5C%22%3Etransferred%3C%2Fa%3E%20Central%20Railway%E2%80%99s%20Public%20Relations%20Officer%20Shivaji%20Manaspure%20against%20the%20backdrop%20that%20it%20was%20Manaspure%E2%80%99s%20deputy%2C%20Abhay%20Mishra%2C%20as%20Deputy%20General%20Manager%20of%20Central%20Railway%2C%20disclosed%20the%20information%20pertaining%20to%20selfie%20points.%20Manaspure%20had%20been%20in%20the%20post%20for%20seven%20months%20while%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20said%20post%20is%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20sought%20to%20underline%20that%20Manaspure%E2%80%99s%20transfer%20was%20done%20as%20an%20act%20of%20punishment%20due%20to%20the%20embarrassment%20caused%20to%20the%20Modi%20government.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EShahenshah%20ki%20raza%2C%20sach%20ka%20inaam%20saza%3C%2Fi%3E%20(King%20rewards%20truth%20with%20punishment)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20had%20written%20on%20X%20(formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20at%20Indian%20Railways%20refute%20the%20allegations%20that%20Manaspure%E2%80%99s%20transfer%20was%20due%20to%20the%20information%20revealed%20on%20selfie%20points.%20They%20say%20it%20was%20only%20due%20to%20operational%20reasons.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20they%20say%20revised%20guidelines%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20RTI%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ajay%20Bose%2C%20a%20former%20railway%20employee%2C%20who%20had%20sought%20information%20on%20selfie%20points%20through%20an%20RTI%20application%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CRTIs%20filed%20to%20seek%20response%20on%20expenditure%20incurred%20%5Bon%20the%203D%20booths%5D%20from%20Southern%2C%20Western%20and%20Northern%20Railways%20did%20not%20elicit%20any%20response.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704351635000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F29112023%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fafter-row-over-pm-selfie-points-railways-tightens-rti-norms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20the%20changed%20rules%2C%20all%20RTI%20replies%20from%20Indian%20Railways%20must%20go%20through%20general%20managers%20of%20zonal%20railways%20or%20divisional%20railway%20managers.%20So%20far%2C%20public%20information%20officers%20and%20chief%20public%20information%20officers%20handled%20the%20matter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagem