20state%20minister%20in%20the%20Naidu%20government%20for%20over%20two%20years.%20His%20was%20a%20launch%20that%20never%20materialised%20as%20effectively%20as%20Naidu%20had%20imagined.%20Murmurs%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20senior%20leaders%20viewed%20Lokesh%E2%80%99s%20sudden%20arrival%20as%20a%20threat%20and%20a%20move%20that%20could%20backfire%20on%20the%20TDP%20became%20stronger%20by%20the%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20the%20drubbing%20that%20Naidu%20and%20his%20party%20faced%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20YSR%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy-led%20YSR%20Congress%20in%20the%202019%20assembly%20polls%20almost%20buried%20all%20hopes%20for%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20rising%20star%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20political%20proscenium.%20Lokesh%20lost%20his%20maiden%20election%20from%20Guntur%E2%80%99s%20Mangalagiri%20narrowly%20to%20the%20YSRCP%20candidate%2C%20even%20as%20his%20party%20was%20reduced%20to%20a%20paltry%2023%20seats%20in%20the%20175-member%20assembly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFive%20years%20down%20the%20line%2C%20however%2C%20the%20state%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20is%20witnessing%20a%20rebirthed%20Lokesh.%20The%20earlier%20shy%20and%20unsure%20Lokesh%2C%20acknowledged%20more%20as%20a%20dynast%20than%20anything%20else%2C%20has%20given%20way%20to%20a%20diligent%20and%20an%20energetic%20leader%20in%20the%20making.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04110714%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-03-at-6.39.24-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04110714%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-03-at-6.39.24-PM.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-conten