20226%20days%20across%20the%20state%2C%20and%20ended%20on%20December%2020%2C%202023%2C%20with%20intermittent%20breaks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20last%20one%20year%2C%20Lokesh%20is%20said%20to%20have%20participated%20in%20around%20200%20public%20meetings%2C%20where%20he%20received%20around%204%2C300%20grievance%20petitions%20from%20the%20public.%20Barring%20a%20two%20month%20break%2C%20when%20Lokesh%20was%20at%20his%20aggressive%20best%20in%20demanding%20a%20bail%20for%20his%20father%20who%20was%20lodged%20in%20prison%2C%20the%2040-year%20old%20TDP%20leader%20has%20walked%20about%2012-15%20kilometres%20everyday%2C%20in%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20mass%20outreach%20ever.%20His%20speeches%20have%20been%20fiercely%20critical%20of%20the%20state%20government%3B%20he%20has%20often%20referred%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%20as%20%E2%80%9Cpsycho%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20reference%20that%20also%20figures%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Epadyatra%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esong%2C%20and%20has%20built%20an%20opposition%20narrative%20around%20over-centralisation%20during%20the%20Jagan%20Reddy%20government%2C%20democratic%20backsliding%20in%20the%20state%2C%20unemployment%2C%20allegedly%20illegal%20sand%20mining%20and%20liquor%20sale%2C%20and%20a%20supposed%20failing%20law%20and%20order%20condition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20503px)%2085vw%2C%20503px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04110736%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-03-at-6.37.48-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22503%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04110736%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-03-at-6.37.48-PM.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04110736%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-03-at-6.37.48-PM-225x300.jpeg%20225w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691561%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22671%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20outskirts%20of%20Visakhapatnam%20on%20December%2018%2C%20during%20the%20Yuvagalam%20rally.%20Photo%3A%20Ajoy%20Ashirwad%20Mahaprashastha%2FThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Epadyatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20itself%20was%20a%20colourful%20affair%2C%20marked%20by%20larger-than-life%20cut-outs%20of%20Lokesh%20and%20Naidu%2C%20an%20enthusiastic%20and%20raucous%20crowd%20looking%20to%20get%20a%20glimpse%20of%20Lokesh%20and%20his%20family%20members%20who%20were%20often%20walking%20alongside.%20It%20was%20as%20much%20a%20mass%20outreach%20as%20much%20as%20it%20was%20an%20unprecedented%20effort%20in%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20absence%20to%20consolidate%20party%20rank%20and%20file.%20More%20importantly%2C%20it%20was%20a%20visible%20instance%20of%20how%20a%20leader%20is%20born%2C%20through%20sheer%20hard%20work%20and%20persistence%2C%20and%20accepted%20by%20people%20as%20one%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20caught%20up%20with%20Lokesh%20on%20December%2018%2C%20two%20days%20before%20it%20culminated%20in%20Visakhapatnam%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Naidu%20and%20his%20ally%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20of%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20party.%20As%20the%20nation%20gears%20up%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Lokesh%20had%20clear%20answers%20about%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20role%2C%20his%20own%20plan%2C%20rumours%20about%20the%20TDP%20joining%20the%20NDA%20ranks%20again%2C%20and%20why%20he%20thinks%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20polls%20is%20almost%20certain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%20is%20an%20excerpt%20from%20the%20interview%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOne%20gets%20an%20impression%20that%20while%20TDP%E2%80%99s%20governance%20centred%20around%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20YSR%20Congress%20has%20a%20focussed%20approach%20towards%20welfare%20of%20the%20poor.%20How%20do%20you%20differentiate%20between%20your%20party%20and%20Jagan%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20balance%20has%20always%20been%20between%20welfare%20and%20development.%20The%20development%20wheel%20in%20the%20cycle%20sort%20of%20loomed%20the%20welfare%20wheel.%20And%20if%20you%20look%20at%20our%20manifesto%20also%2C%20we%20have%20said%20that%20we%20will%20create%2020%20lakh%20jobs%20for%20the%20youth.%20So%20if%20you%20have%20to%20create%2020%20lakh%20jobs%2C%20and%20as%20and%20when%20we%20create%2020%20lakh%20jobs%2C%20Andhra%E2%80%99s%20economy%20will%20triple.%20So%2C%20based%20on%20the%20past%2C%20every%20six%20lakh%20jobs%20doubles%20the%20economic%20growth.%20That%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20work%20that%20we%20want%20to%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20number%20of%20companies%20that%20have%20come%20to%20our%20state%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20development%20that%20has%20happened%2C%20our%20reforms%2C%20all%20that%20was%20done%20by%20Mr.%20Naidu.%20But%20we%20also%20believe%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20balanced%20by%20welfare.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20this%20government%20has%20specifically%20done%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20have%20done%20welfare%20on%20the%20back%20of%20debt%20and%20that%20has%20resulted%20in%20substantial%20increase%20in%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20current%20prices%20have%20gone%20up%20nine%20times%2C%20power%20prices%20up%20by%20nine%20times.%20Petrol%2C%20diesel%20prices%20are%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20country.%20Welfare%20based%20on%20debt%20money%20is%20a%20wrong%20approach.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAndhra%20is%20in%20that%20(debt)%20trap%20and%20people%20have%20recognised%20that.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20something%20that%20we%20will%20break%2C%20we%20will%20break%20that%20cycle.%20We%E2%80%99ll%20put%20the%20state%20back%20on%20the%20development%20platform.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnaidus-arrest-what-is-the-andhra-pradesh-skill-development-scam%5C%22%3ETDP%20Sets%20Up%20Website%20to%20Counter%20Skill%20Development%20Scheme%20Charges%2C%20Highlights%20Praise%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThis%20(%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3Epadyatra%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E)%20song%20that%20I%20was%20just%20listening%20to%20named%20the%20chief%20minister%20as%20%E2%80%98the%20psycho.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20chief%20minister%2C%20once%20he%20comes%20into%20power%2C%20would%20always%20like%20to%20start%20work%20on%20a%20development%20and%20welfare%20platform.%20But%20what%20he%20started%20on%20was%20the%20destruction%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eprajavedika%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20subsequently%20all%20the%20issues%20that%20he%20has%20taken%20on%20have%20just%20ruined%20the%20state.%20So%20if%20you%20look%20at%20our%20economy%2C%20power%20sector%2C%20agri-sector%2C%20mining%2C%20sand%2C%20every%20sector%20is%20ruined.%20So%2C%20people%20have%20started%20to%20call%20him%20a%20psycho.%20So%20this%20kind%20of%20psychotic%20behaviour%20will%20lead%20to%20him%20being%20called%20psycho.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20know%2C%20he%20says%20he%20has%20no%20money%20to%20make%20even%20one%20capital%20(city)%2C%20but%20he%20has%20money%20to%20do%20three%20capitals.%20How%20is%20it%20going%20to%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20do%20you%20measure%20the%20success%20of%20your%20padayatra%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20if%20I%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20success%2C%20you%20will%20say%2C%20obviously%20Lokesh%20will%20claim%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20success%2C%20right.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENo%2C%20but%20I%20will%20listen%20to%20you.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20will%20not%20claim%20anything.%20I%20think%20it%20is%20for%20you%20to%20judge%20whether%20Yuvagalam%20is%20a%20success%20or%20not.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20my%20perspective%2C%20the%20entire%20reason%20why%20I%20started%20the%20padayatra%20is%20to%20give%20a%20platform%20for%20youth%20to%20talk%20about%20their%20problems.%20But%20then%20in%20a%20month%2C%2045%20days%20into%20the%20padayatra%2C%20you%20know%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20youth%2C%20but%20every%20section%20of%20society%20has%20been%20troubled%20and%20this%20Yuvagalam%20has%20become%20Andhra%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egalam%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(voice).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20manifested%20into%20the%20farmers%20talking%20about%20their%20problems%2C%20women%20talking%20about%20their%20problems%2C%20youngsters%20talking%20about%20their%20problems%2C%20students%20talking%20about%20their%20problems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20end%2C%20you%20know%2C%20we%20realised%20that%2C%20you%20know%2C%20this%20person%20is%20just%20all%20talk%20but%20no%20work%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20something%20that%E2%80%99s%20come%20out%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20padayatra%2C%20women%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20day%2C%20have%20come%20out%2C%20volunteered%20and%20they%20stood%20there%2C%20received%20us%2C%20explained%20their%20problems%20and%2C%20you%20know%2C%20sort%20of%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20what%20they%20expect%20from%20our%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIn%20terms%20of%20social%20outreach%2C%20how%20successful%20has%20it%20been%3F%20Because%20the%20last%20time%20the%20results%20showed%20that%20the%20TDP%20had%20lost%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20its%20traditional%20voters%20to%20this%20YSRCP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20number%20of%20seats%2C%20YSRCP%20won%20151%20and%20we%20won%2023.%20But%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20we%20got%2040%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share%20and%20YSRCP%20got%2050%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share.%20So%2C%20I%20need%20to%20convince%206%20in%20100%20to%20vote%20for%20TDP%20to%20win%20with%20a%20simple%20majority.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20has%20happened%20is%20Jagan%2C%20psycho%20Jagan%20as%20we%20fondly%20call%20him%2C%20came%20on%20a%20promise%20of%20one%20chance.%20He%20said%20he%20will%20change%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%2C%20that%20he%20is%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20son.%20But%20what%20people%20have%20realised%20is%20that%20their%20lives%20have%20become%20worse%20off%20and%20he%20has%20done%20nothing%20but%20ruin%20their%20lives.%20All%20the%20promises%20that%20he%20made%20for%20various%20communities%2C%20caste-wise%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20fructified.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBut%20he%20has%20five%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20from%20different%20communities.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20what%20power%20do%20they%20have%3F%20You%20know%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20Dalit.%20But%20she%20cannot%20protect%20Dalits%20in%20her%20own%20constituency%20from%20YSRCP%20leaders.%20Giving%20posts%20does%20not%20change%20things%20sir%2C%20empowering%20people%20changes%20things.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%E2%80%99re%20all%20dummies.%20My%20question%20to%20Jagan%20is%20that%20why%20have%20you%20cancelled%2027%20welfare%20programmes%20of%20Dalits%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EYou%20allege%20that%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20power%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I%20said%2C%20even%20the%20Dalit%20home%20minister%20is%20not%20allowed%20into%20the%20Dalit%20area%20of%20a%20village.%20She%20is%20a%20home%20minister.%20What%20can%20she%20do%20tomorrow%20then%3F%20See%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20in%20the%20state%20no%2C%20all%20the%20ministers%20are%20dummies.%20All%20the%20deputy%20CMs%20are%20dummies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20432px)%2085vw%2C%20432px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04110705%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-03-at-6.40.34-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22432%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04110705%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-03-at-6.40.34-PM.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04110705%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-03-at-6.40.34-PM-225x300.jpeg%20225w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691558%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20outskirts%20of%20Visakhapatnam%20on%20December%2018%2C%20during%20the%20Yuvagalam%20rally.%20Photo%3A%20Ajoy%20Ashirwad%20Mahaprashastha%2FThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMany%20of%20your%20father%E2%80%99s%20pet%20projects%20are%20stuck%20now%20%E2%80%93%20Polavaram%2C%20capital%2C%20all%20of%20them%20are%20stuck.%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStuck%2C%20I%20think%2C%20is%20a%20very%20soft%20word.%20Ruined%20is%20the%20right%20word.%20See%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20easy%20to%20ruin%20things.%20It%E2%80%99s%20very%20difficult%20to%20build.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20minister%2C%20Mr.%20Anil%20Yadav%2C%20said%20in%202021%20that%20they%E2%80%99ll%20finish%20Polavaram.%20It%E2%80%99s%20already%202024.%20Mr.%20Naidu%20finished%20the%20work%20up%20to%2072%25.%20I%20think%20these%20guys%20have%20done%20another%204%25%20in%20four%20years.%20Amaravati%20stands%20in%20ruins.%20They%20have%20done%20nothing%20to%20Visakhapatnam%20which%20they%20claim%20is%20an%20executive%20capital.%20In%20the%20Judiciary%20capital%2C%20Kurnool%2C%20they%20have%20not%20even%20done%20any%20land%20acquisition%20for%20the%20high%20court%20to%20be%20built.%20They%20have%20not%20even%20sent%20a%20request%20to%20CJI%20to%20shift%20the%20high%20court.%20The%20chief%20justice%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20has%20not%20received%20any%20request.%20So%20there%E2%80%99s%20nothing%20but%20playing%20with%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EYour%20party%20faced%20the%20worst%20drubbing%20in%20the%20Rayalseema%20area.%20How%20do%20you%20assess%20your%20situation%20this%20time%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20last%20time%20in%20Rayalaseema%2C%20we%20won%20only%20three%20seats.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20be%20surprised%20this%20time%20if%20we%20win%2080%25%20of%20the%20seats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBecause%20you%20started%20your%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3Epadyatra%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3Efrom%20the%20region%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20spent%20most%20of%20my%20time%20in%20Rayalaseema.%20The%20entire%20summer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAccess%20to%20water%20was%20a%20huge%20problem%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20like%20a%20problem%20there%20since%20ever.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbsolutely.%20And%20that%20is%20what%2C%20Polavaram%20would%20have%20been%20completed.%20Water%20could%20have%20come%2C%20you%20know%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20project%20called%20Pattiseema.%20Pattiseema%20was%20a%20temporary%20project%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20expensive%20project.%201700%20crores%20was%20spent%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20expensive%20project.%20The%20idea%20is%20we%20will%20take%20water%20from%20Godavari%2C%20give%20it%20to%20Krishna%20Delta%2C%20from%20where%20it%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20Rayalaseema.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20whole%20idea.%20And%20Mr.%20Naidu%20worked%20on%20it%20for%20three%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20chief%20minister%2C%20simply%20because%20he%20opposed%20Pattiseema%20for%20whatever%20reason%2C%20refused%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20motors%20of%20Pattiseema.%20And%20he%20dried%20Rayalseema%20and%20dried%20Krishna%20delta.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20in%20Rayalaseema%2C%20you%20know%2C%20despite%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20large%20number%20of%20ministers%2C%20water%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20problem.%20Lack%20of%20industrialization%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20problem.%20And%20when%20I%20walked%20in%2C%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20my%20selfies%20came%20from%20Rayalaseema.%20That%E2%80%99s%20an%20acknowledgement%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20got%20industries%20in%20Rayalaseema.%20So%20we%20are%20proud%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESo%20are%20you%20still%20calling%20for%20some%20kind%20of%20special%20category%20status%20for%20AP%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20ask%20for%20it.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%2C%20right.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20the%20(special)%20category%20status%2C%20we%20continue%20to%20ask%20for%20the%20demands%2C%20the%20promises%20made%20in%20the%20bifurcation%20to%20be%20met.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20YSRCP%20has%2022%20MPs%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20talk%2C%20they%20have%209%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%2C%20they%20never%20raise%20their%20voice%20for%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBut%2C%20politically%2C%20you%20will%20have%20to%20stitch%20a%20social%20coalition%20to%20win.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETDP%20does%20not%20believe%20in%20talks%20based%20on%20caste%2C%20creed%2C%20religion.%20We%20believe%20that%20we%20need%20to%20develop%20the%20state%2C%20we%20need%20to%20eliminate%20poverty.%20And%20TDP%20is%20known%20for%20it.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20balance%20both%20welfare%20and%20development.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBut%20social%20outreach%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20cornerstone.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20our%20promises%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20quite%20clear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20always%20a%20%3Cem%3EKamma%3C%2Fem%3E%20(caste)%20party%20tag%20to%20shed%20though.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20disagree.%20I%E2%80%99m%20sorry%20but%20if%20you%20look%20at%20it%2C%20even%20before%20TDP%20was%20founded%2C%20there%20were%20close%20to%2067%20Kamma%20MLAs%20in%20294%20assembly%20seats%20of%20combined%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20This%20is%20the%20pre-TDP%20era.%20Post%20TDP%20era%2C%20that%20number%20of%20seats%20have%20come%20down.%20The%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%E2%80%99s%20success%20was%20because%20of%20the%20role%20that%20the%20BCs%20(backward%20communities)%20played%20in%20its%20emergence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWho%20was%20our%20finance%20minister%3F%20Who%20was%20our%20revenue%20minister%3F%20Who%20was%20our%20I%26amp%3BB%20minister%3F%20All%20the%20major%20key%20portfolios%20were%20held%20by%20BC%20leaders.%20I%20mean%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20deputy%20chairperson%20of%20our%20council%2C%20he%20was%20a%20BC.%20Deputy%20speakers%20were%20BCs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJagan%20has%20been%20lying%20about%20our%20party.%20He%20lied%20to%20the%20president%20of%20India.%20He%20lied%20to%20the%20governor.%20He%20lied%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20I%E2%80%99ll%20tell%20you%20why.%20He%20is%20a%20pathological%20liar.%20It%E2%80%99s%20very%20unfair%20that%20even%20media%20makes%20such%20a%20claim.%20Please%20look%20at%20the%20data.%20Please%20look%20at%20our%20leadership.%20Please%20look%20at%20our%20Politburo.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlease%20look%20at%20every%20body%20in%20Telugu%20Desam%20since%20its%20foundation%2C%20since%20its%20inception%20and%20it%20has%20(the%20BC%20representation)%20been%20extremely%20strong.%20This%20time%2C%20we%20plan%20to%20send%20more%20BCs%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20the%20assembly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStill%2C%20the%20larger%20question%20is%20whether%20Jagan%E2%80%99s%20minist