20against%20the%20psycho%20government.%20That%20much%20is%20quite%20clear.%20It%20is%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20decide%20whether%20they%20would%20like%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%20alliance%20or%20not.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESo%20many%2C%20many%20people%20say%20that%20Jagan%20check-mated%20the%20TDP%20by%20preventing%20it%20from%20aligning%20itself%20with%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%20will%20now%20have%20to%20answer%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20if%20it%20allies%20with%20Naidu%20who%20is%20facing%20corruption%20charges.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsn%E2%80%99t%20it%20ironic%20that%20we%20are%20having%20this%20conversation%3F%20Jagan%20has%2038%20cases%20against%20him%20%E2%80%93%2011%20CBI%2C%207%20ED.%20Rs%2043%2C000%20crores%20of%20public%20money%20was%20swindled%20by%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EI%20was%20saying%20that%20Jagan%20was%20kind%20of%20trying%20to%20put%20BJP%20in%20a%20spot%2C%20not%20TDP.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShow%20me%20one%20national%20leader%20who%20believes%20Mr.%20Naidu%20is%20corrupt.%20Just%20because%20if%20a%20madman%20falsely%20accused%20Mr.%20Naidu%2C%20manages%20all%20the%20institutions%2C%20sends%20him%20to%20judicial%20remand%20for%2053%20days%2C%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20him%20a%20corrupt%20politician.%20I%20mean%2C%20where%20is%20the%20proof%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20know%2C%20what%20did%20they%20say%3F%203000%20crores%20scam%20in%20skill%20development%2C%20then%20they%20said%20370%20crore.%20Now%20they%E2%80%99re%20saying%2027%20crore.%20I%20said%2C%20prove%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20unable%20to%20prove.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%E2%80%99re%20telling%20me%20a%20man%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%2015%20years%2C%20spent%2015%20years%20as%20leader%20of%20opposition%20has%20indulged%20in%20a%20corruption%20scam%20worth%20only%20Rs%2027%20crores.%20We%20still%20say%20that%20the%20skill%20development%20programme%20in%20our%20government%20helped%20train%202%2C15%2C000%20kids%20and%20get%2085%2C000%20people%20jobs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20irony%20is%20that%20after%20Mr.%20Naidu%20came%20out%2C%20I%20restarted%20my%20padayatra%20in%20East%20Godavari%20where%20I%20received%20about%20six%20representations%20to%20intensify%20our%20skill%20development%20programme.%20I%20told%20them%20this%20is%20the%20reason%20Mr.%20Naidu%20was%20sent%20to%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimply%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20tell%20you%2C%20if%20Mr.%20Naidu%20wanted%20to%20make%20money%2C%20he%20knew%20Cyberabad%20was%20coming%20up.%20He%20knew%20the%20value%20of%20land%20in%20Hyderabad%20would%20go%20up.%20Back%20then%2C%20the%20value%20per%20acre%20was%20not%20more%20than%20a%20lakh%20of%20rupees.%20Mr.%20Naidu%20could%20have%20purchased%20a%20minimum%201%2C000%20acres.%20No%20one%20could%20have%20questioned%20that.%20He%20would%20have%20been%20worth%20nothing%20less%20than%20%24%2010-12%20billion%20dollars%20today%2C%20if%20he%20did%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpurandeswari-andhra-pradesh-bjp-chief-tdp-growth%5C%22%3EBy%20Appointing%20Purandeswari%20as%20Andhra%20Chief%2C%20Is%20BJP%20Trying%20to%20Grow%20at%20TDP%E2%80%99s%20Expense%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESimilar%20charges%20were%20filed%20against%20him%20in%20Amaravati%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20know%2C%20on%20one%20side%2C%20they%20say%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20house%20in%20Amaravati.%20On%20the%20other%20side%2C%20they%20say%20that%20I%20had%20insider%20information%20and%20my%20company%20bought%20land%20which%20is%2090%20kilometres%20away%20or%20X%20kilometres%20away%20from%20the%20core%20capital.%20Absolutely%20rubbish%20charges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWill%20your%20party%20or%20your%20father%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%3F%20He%20was%20a%20part%20of%20that%20opposition%20in%202019.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistorically%2C%20TDP%20has%20been%20an%20anti-Congress%20platform%2C%20because%20we%20believe%20the%20leadership%20of%20Congress%20did%20not%20do%20justice%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Mr.%20Naidu%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20United%20Front%20government%2C%20and%20subsequently%20was%20the%20NDA%20convenor%20also%20under%20Vajpayee%20ji%E2%80%99s%20tenure.%20Vajpayee%20ji%20was%20very%20kind%20enough%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20good%20work%20for%20Andhra%20and%20the%20nation%2C%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20fact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20our%20stand%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20same%20as%20of%20now.%20We%E2%80%99re%20equidistant%20from%20both%20alliances%20and%20our%20support%20is%20purely%20issue-based.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESo%2C%20will%20TDP%20not%20compromise%20its%20secular%20fundamentals%20in%20case%20it%20supports%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP.%C2%A0%20Continue%20its%20inclusive%20secular%20politics%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETDP%E2%80%99s%20fundamentals%2C%20foundation%20is%20based%20on%20secularism.%20The%20first%20Dalit%20speaker%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20a%20person%20from%20TDP%2C%20(G.M.C)%20Balayogi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20right%3F%20The%20first%20woman%20Dalit%20speaker%20in%20the%20assembly%20is%20a%20TDPian.%20(K.)%20Pratibha%20Bharati%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20First%20minority%20person%20that%20went%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20was%20(S.M)%20Laljan%20Basha%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20Guntur.%20So%2C%20TDP%20believes%20that%20India%20should%20not%20be%20divided%20along%20religious%20lines.%20We%20are%20a%20union%20of%20states.%20Together%2C%20we%20need%20to%20move%20forward.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20secularism%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20we%20are%20anti-Hinduism.%20I%20think%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20fine%20line.%20When%20this%20(state)%20government%20got%20formed%2C%20attacks%20on%20temples%20increased.%20And%20in%20Ram%20Tirtham%2C%20which%20is%20a%20very%20historical%20temple%20in%20North%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20idol%20was%20defaced%20and%20Mr.%20Naidu%20went%20there.%20And%20people%20questioned%20me%20and%20I%20asked%20a%20straight%20question%20to%20everyone%20that%20if%20this%20had%20happened%20to%20a%20mosque%2C%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20any%20political%20party%20respond%3F%20The%20same%20thing%20happened%20to%20a%20church%20and%20we%20responded.%20TDP%20is%20a%20secular%20party.%20We%20stand%20by%20Hindus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20do%20you%20weigh%20your%20chances%20in%20these%20elections%3F%20Both%20in%20parliament%20and%20assembly%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20victory%20is%20a%20virtual%20certainty.%20We%20will%20sweep%20all%20regions%2C%20just%20wait%20and%20watch.%20I%20sensed%20anti-incumbency%20against%20Jagan%E2%80%99s%20government%20as%20early%20as%20October%202021.%20That%20is%20when%2C%20in%20my%20own%20constituency%2C%20I%20started%20doing%20a%20door-to-door%20programme%20and%20I%20reported%20back%20to%20Mr.%20Naidu%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20severe%20anti-incumbency%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20did%20this%20programme%20on%20price%20rise%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth.%20And%20then%20we%20did%20a%20programme%20on%20the%2C%20you%20know%2C%20what%20is%20the%20sorry%20state%20of%20this%20Andhra%20Pradesh%3F%20And%20now%20we%20are%20doing%20a%20programme%20on%20welfare.%20We%E2%80%99re%20going%20to%20do%20a%20programme%20on%20hope.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESo%20you%E2%80%99ve%20been%20active%20all%20these%20five%20years%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20you%20should%20ask%20the%20public.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESince%20January%2C%20I%20know%20that%20you%E2%80%99ve%20been%20doing%20this%20padayatra.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%2022%20cases%20against%20me.%20I%20have%20an%20attempt%20to%20murder%20case%20against%20me%2C%20I%20have%20an%20SC-ST%20atrocity%20case%20against%20me.%20If%20I%20was%20an%20inactive%20politician%20or%20a%20part-time%20politician%2C%20do%20you%20think%20so%20many%20cases%20would%20be%20there%3F%20And%20by%20the%20way%2C%20quite%20a%20few%20people%20sitting%20here%20have%20cases%20against%20them%20also.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20Andhra%20feature.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%2C%20no%2C%20that%20is%20a%20very%20psycho%20Jagan%20feature.%20When%20Mr.%20Naidu%20was%20in%20power%2C%20he%20did%20not%20harass%20Jagan.%20In%20fact%2C%20Jagan%20was%20postponing%20his%20cases.%20You%20know%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20led%20to%20believe%20Raghuram%20Krishnam%20Raju%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20He%E2%80%99s%20YSRCP%E2%80%99s%20own%20MP%3B%20he%20claims%20Jagan%20has%20asked%20for%20adjournment%20in%20his%20cases%204%2C000%20times.%20And%20Mr.%20Naidu%2C%20when%20he%20was%20in%20the%20government%2C%20never%20fast-tracked%20his%20cases.%20Mr.%20Naidu%20never%20practised%20vendetta%20politics%20either%20on%20Jagan%20or%20even%20his%20father%2C%20YSR.%20He%20ever%20did.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20when%20YSR%20had%20a%20life%20threat%2C%20you%20know%2C%20from%20some%20elements%2C%20it%20was%20Mr.%20Naidu%20who%20gave%20him%20security.%20This%20was%20pre-2004.%20That%20is%20what%20Mr%20Naidu%20stands%20for.%20In%20the%20five%20years%20of%20our%20administration%2C%20it%20was%20all%20about%20development%20and%20welfare.%20Otherwise%20why%20would%20so%20many%20companies%20come%20to%20Andhra%3F%20Why%20would%20Kia%20come%2C%20Foxconn%20come%2C%20TCL%20come%2C%20and%20then%20HCL%2C%20Zoho%2C%20Asian%20Paints%2C%20Berger%20Paints%2C%20Apollo%20Tyres%2C%20Hero%20Motors%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20vision%20is%20also%20the%20same.%20Since%20January%2027%2C%20last%20year%2C%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20taken%20a%20break%20even%20on%20Saturdays%20and%20Sundays.%20The%20only%20breaks%20in%20this%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eyatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20during%20festivals%20because%20our%20leaders%20asked%20me%20to%20do%20so.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20a%20break%20except%20when%20Mr.%20Naidu%20was%20in%20judicial%20remand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOrganisationally%2C%20are%20you%20appearing%20to%20be%20deep%20rooted%20now%3F%20You%20have%20been%20credited%20with%20increasing%20party%20membership%20by%20quite%20a%20few%20times%20through%20your%20digital%20outreach%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETDP%20has%20always%20been%20an%20organisationally%20strong%20party%2C%20but%20TDP%20is%20also%20like%20an%20elephant.%20If%20it%20sits%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stand.%20If%20it%20stands%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20run.%20Once%20it%20runs%2C%20anyone%20who%20comes%20opposite%20to%20it%2C%20it%20will%20just%20stomp%20him%20and%20go%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20kind%20of%20momentum%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20are%20your%20challenges%20ahead%20of%20elections%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20think%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20we%20will%20face%20is%20misuse%20of%20official%20missionary.%20But%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20reach%20every%20household%20and%20we%20are%20giving%20them%20a%20bond%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20we%20are%20going%20to%20do%20once%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20comes%20back%20to%20power.%20So%20we%20have%20a%20very%20strong%20grassroots%20organisation%2C%20in%20that%20sense.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704349816000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04110744%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-03-at-6.45.06-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-telugu-desam-party-nara-lokesh-jaganmohan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2