%20hold%20in%202013.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20done%20over%201%2C400%20surgeries%20and%20with%20my%20knowledge%20of%20robotic%20surgeries%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20use%20my%20life%20savings%20of%204.5%20million%20dollars%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Germany%20to%20meet%20some%20of%20their%20scientists%20for%20an%20exchange%20of%20technology.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20not%20a%20success.%20Then%2C%20I%20came%20back%20to%20India%20and%20formed%20a%20team%20of%2010%20engineers%20and%20started%20the%20development%20out%20of%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20robotic%20surgeries%20and%20how%20do%20they%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sudhir%20explains%20why%20robotic%20surgeries%20are%20important.%20%E2%80%9CDepth%2C%20precision%20and%20safety.%20These%20are%20three%20things%20that%20surmise%20why%20we%20need%20robotic%20surgeries.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20technology%2C%20the%20surgeon%20gets%20an%20in-depth%20picture%20of%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20parts%20to%20be%20operated%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-4-1700577778.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20technology%20has%20successfully%20assisted%20doctors%20in%20performing%20500%20surgeries%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-4-1700577778.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-4-1700577778-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-4-1700577778-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-4-1700577778-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%